Cax max yalon xal bay cham yetbi tuꞌ axca tiꞌ:
A jun in trato chi wakꞌ etok tiꞌ, cꞌal yetok masanil eb enatil tuꞌ yin tojbalkꞌinal, tol a Diosal in, cꞌal is Diosal in eb.
