20-21 A Dios max colwajcꞌal yetok nak unin tuꞌ, cax max chꞌibcꞌal aj nak. Max ayjicꞌal ecꞌ nak bay tzꞌinan txꞌotxꞌ bay yul yet Parán; julom noꞌ max elocok. Axa max yun xin, max mojay nak yetok jun ix aj Egipto yuj is txutx.
