Max apni oc bay jun lugar, a bay tuꞌ max can yet akꞌbalil, yujtol mayal ay cꞌu. Axa yet toxa chi way xin, cax max yiontek jun chꞌen chꞌen bay tuꞌ is kꞌanok, axa yay telan way tuꞌ.
