Max naon ba cꞌul Raquel, yujtol cꞌamcꞌal yuneꞌ xal chi yilaꞌ, axa cꞌoli chichon oc cꞌul xal yin xal Lea tuꞌ, max yalon bay yetbi tuꞌ axca tiꞌ:
A yet max jay jun is babel unin xal max yaloni: Mayal yiel Jehová qꞌuixwilal ayoc win, yuj mayal yakꞌ jun wuneꞌ tiꞌ.
Ayex tiꞌ caw wal e yojtak sicꞌlibil tol max in mulnaj bay e mam yin watxꞌil axca wal bay max jeꞌ wuj.
Max octok cham Labán bay is mantiado Jacob, cax max oc cꞌapax bay is mantiado Lea, cꞌal bay is mantiado eb ix cawan chekbej, palta cꞌamcꞌal tzet max ilchaj yuj. Lajwi yeltek yul is mantiado xal Lea cax max octok bay is mantiado Raquel.
Lajwi tuꞌ max yakꞌon cham Jacob is tiꞌ yin bi Dios bay chi oc Isaac is mam yin ayilal yetok.
Axa yet max cancan cham Jacob is txꞌoklil, max yakꞌlej owal yetok jun winak masantacꞌal max sakbi.
Palta a cham Jacob max occꞌal ijan yin yalon axca tiꞌ:
