—Ayin ton Jehová in. Al bay cham reyal Egipto masanil tzet chi wal ayach tiꞌ, ẍi Cham.
Yet is suk cꞌualxa yetaxtok aꞌ aej yuj Jehová,
—A yet yecal yet puch kꞌinibalilto chi toj jun rey tuꞌ bay ti aꞌ aej, yuj tu xin, chach pet aj wanok, cax chi toj alon bay: Axca tiꞌ yalon Jehová: Cha bekil in conob yet chi oc eb yin ayilal ayin.
Axa eb tzꞌakan cꞌul, majxa jeꞌ txꞌoxon ba eb satak Moisés, yujtol yaꞌay eb yuj yabil axca yayji masanil eb anima bay Egipto.
—As il jun rey tuꞌ, max wakꞌ pitbok el is nabal yetok eb ay yopiso yetok, yet watxꞌ chi yil eb masanil seña cꞌayubtakxacꞌal chi wunej,
—A tinaniꞌ, i pax aj a kꞌab can, yet watxꞌ chi kꞌekkꞌolil bay masanil yul yet nación Egipto tiꞌ. Caw wal junelnej tol kꞌekkꞌolinak ok yuncan elok, ẍi Jehová.
A no noꞌ tuꞌ achꞌej calnel ma achꞌej chiwo, yowalil tol jun abil is kꞌinal, cax cꞌam jabok is tacnakil noꞌ.
Ajun eb aj Egipto tuꞌ max chekon el eb israel, yet chi el eb yin aymanil yul is conobal, yujtol max na eb talaj chi cam eb masanil.
Yuj tu xin, junjuncꞌal abil ok co chaon jun kꞌin tiꞌ yet jun xajaw tiꞌ.
