A yet max a xuontok a cakꞌekꞌ yiban aꞌ mar, cax max mukaycantok eb nak yuj aꞌ; max tojcan eb nak yich aꞌ axca chꞌen plomo.
Cax max yaloncꞌal cham Moisés:
Maná max yakꞌ eb israel yik juntzan is lobej eb max wajaj tuꞌ; axca wal sat culantro sak yili, caw wal chiꞌ loji, axca ixim kꞌoxox pan tol ayoc yalcab yin.
Max lajwi tuꞌ, cax max watxꞌnen aj cham Moisés jun altar, cax max yakꞌon yik: A ton Jehová in bandera.
