Axa chꞌen trompeta xin, junjuntak el chi xulay chꞌen, chi tecꞌal aj can nukꞌ, a ton yet tuꞌ max kꞌanjab Moisés yetok Dios, caw wal ip chi yut takꞌwok ba Cham bay.
