Masanil eb xal aj bal, yowalil chi cam eb xal.
A yet xajaw Abib, che chaon kꞌinal ixim pan tol cꞌam yich, axca max wut walon ayex, tol a yin ukeb cꞌual che loꞌ ixim pan tol cꞌam yich; yujtol a yet jun xajaw tuꞌ, max ex el bay Egipto. Cꞌam junok mac chi jay in satak yin tol cꞌam jabok ofrenda ibil oc yuj.
—Masanil tzet chi yal Jehová, chi jaoc yin co cꞌul jikeni, ẍi eb.
A bay yul teꞌ tuꞌ ok acan aytok chꞌen chꞌen bay ayoc in trato ok wakꞌ ayach.
