Axa bay tiꞌ in cajlobal tu xin, a tuꞌ chi watxꞌji oc junok an cortina yetok yax txꞌal, an txꞌal púrpura, cak txꞌal, yetok an lino txꞌumbil; tzꞌisbil cꞌapax oc is yelbub yuj junok jelan tzꞌisoni.
Chi watxꞌji cꞌapax jun cꞌalilej yet chi cꞌal-lay oc jun chaleco tuꞌ; junnejcꞌal chi yun yetok; a jun tuꞌ oro txꞌal, yax txꞌal, txꞌal púrpura, cak txꞌal, cꞌal yetok lino txꞌumbil chi oc yin.
Chakꞌ watxꞌjok junokxa an pichilej yelxacꞌal jokan, tol a wal lino watxꞌ chi oc yin; lino cꞌapax junok kꞌoxilej txꞌumbil chi watxꞌji. Acꞌalaꞌ an cꞌalilej, watxꞌ chi yun yoc cꞌapax is tzꞌibil yuj junok jelan tzꞌisoni.
Cheontek txamcꞌul no calnel ay yopiso, yuj yoccan yikbej yuj Aarón, chi batxon aj in satak; et chi yuncan jun makan no chibej tuꞌ.
Max kꞌanjab Jehová bay Moisés, max yalon bay axca tiꞌ:
Mayal wakꞌ Wespíritu yin is nabal, yet watxꞌ ay is jelanil yin ojtakbilal, cꞌal yajnabalil, yet ok jeꞌ watxꞌnen aj tzancꞌal tzetak yetal,
A tinaniꞌ xin, jitz el a ba yul in be, tol lanan in kꞌakꞌbi tit wowal yin juntzan anima tiꞌ. Ok wakꞌ cꞌayil eb masanil, asan etok ok in watxꞌnej jun miman conob yuj eb onenal, ẍi Jehová.
—Caw wal miman e mul max e yaocok. A tinaniꞌ, tiꞌ chin toj pax bay jolom witz junelxa bay ayicꞌ Jehová. A bay tuꞌ ok in kꞌanjab yetok Cham, axtawal xin, ok yakꞌ tan Cham e mul tuꞌ e yiban, ẍi cham Moisés.
Max takꞌwi Jehová bay cham:
A yet mayal eqꞌuel ukeb semana yecꞌ kꞌin tiꞌ, chaek jun kꞌin yet che yion el ixim trigo babel chi kꞌanbi. Chaek cꞌapax junxa kꞌin yet chi lajwi yaj ixim yet lajub abil.
jun altar bay chi tzꞌa xajanbal, cꞌal is rejail naba bronce, yetokcꞌal is reglail, yetok masanil is mitxꞌkꞌabil, cꞌal yetok jun palangana yetok is batxlubal,
Max lajwi tuꞌ, max tzꞌislay oc xoyjab yax txꞌal yin is tiꞌ an babel jenan tuꞌ yuj mitxꞌbanilok. Acꞌalaꞌ caytuꞌ max yun yoc cꞌapax yin is tiꞌ junxa jenan yet is cab tuꞌ.
Max watxꞌji cꞌapax caneb argolla naba oro chi oc yin yakan canebal, cax cabcab yin junjun pacꞌ.
Cax max watxꞌji cꞌapax oc jun rejail altar tuꞌ tol naba bronce. A bay yalan is tiꞌ max oqui, a tuꞌ chi apni bay is nan jun altar tuꞌ.
Max chacꞌlay patxay chꞌen oro; cocꞌxacꞌal max yun cꞌupon coj eb, axcaxacꞌal txꞌal max yunej yet chi jeꞌ chemontok eb xol juntzanxa txꞌal, max chemlay yuj junok tol watxꞌ chemwi.
Tix masanil is mitxꞌkꞌabil is cajlobal Dios max yitok eb bay cham Moisés tiꞌ: A ton is ganchoal, chemteal, reglail, yoyal cꞌal yetok is batxbanil.
Max lajwi tu xin, max yaon aytok cham Moisés chꞌen cab jenan chꞌen yul caẍa, a ton chꞌen bay tzꞌibbil oc lajoneb mandamiento, a ton is trato Dios, cax max alay oc teꞌ is reglail te caẍa tuꞌ, max alay cꞌapax oc is makil teꞌ yuj cham bay chi akꞌlay tan mulej.
Chi lajwi tuꞌ cax chi cocꞌ tzocꞌnelaytok noꞌ, axa cham sacerdote chi aon ajtok no cocꞌ tzocꞌxa yayji tuꞌ tzꞌa yiban kꞌakꞌ bay yiban altar, yetok no jolomej, cꞌal no sebo chi el yin no yulcꞌulej.
A junok mactxel chi yakꞌ junok xajanbal tuꞌ, chi yiel junok makan yin no xajanbal tuꞌ yet chi akꞌlay tzꞌa satak Jehová, a ton juntzan tiꞌ: a seboal ne noꞌ, watxꞌ chi yun yilay el masanil, cꞌal sebo ayoc yin yul cꞌul noꞌ,
Ta a junok eb yajaw yayji, chi oc is mul yuj tenon junok chekbanil Jehová co Diosal, a jun tuꞌ chi oc is mulok, caxcꞌal man yinok is cꞌul chi tita.
Ta ay junok mac chi oc is mul yin chekbanilej max yakꞌ Jehová, caxcꞌal man yinok cꞌul chi tita, a jun tuꞌ ayxa oc is mulok.
A jun xajanbal tiꞌ yet Jehová yayji. Tzancꞌal mac winakil cajan ecꞌ yetok junok sacerdote yul yatut chi jeꞌ chioni.
Max kꞌanjab Jehová bay cham Moisés, max yalon axca tiꞌ:
Max cocꞌ tzocꞌnentok cham noꞌ, max yakꞌon tzꞌa is jolom noꞌ yetokcꞌal noꞌ cocꞌ yayji tuꞌ, cꞌal yetok seboal noꞌ.
Max txꞌajlay no yulcꞌulej, cꞌal no xubej yetok yakan, axa yakꞌlay cꞌapax tzꞌa bay altar tuꞌ, yiban noꞌ lanan tzꞌaꞌi.
Axa pax no txamcꞌulej chi batxlay ecꞌ satak Jehová yetok no xubej, chi ilay el yin noꞌ, a juntzan tuꞌ e yetcꞌaltaꞌ yayji ocok. A tuꞌ cha chiꞌ yetok eb a cꞌajol cꞌal eb a cutzꞌin bay junok lugar tol watxꞌ yayji, yujtol a juntzan tuꞌ e yetcꞌaltaꞌ yayji yin xajanbal yet juncꞌulalil chi yakꞌ masanil eb jet israelal.
