Lajan wal yayji e conob axca junok ix kꞌopoj ix tol bekbilcan yuj yichamil, tol ayoc yin cuscꞌulal, caytuꞌ yayji. Axa tinaniꞌ, chi awtelay junelxa yuj yichamil tuꞌ.
Chi wal cꞌapax bay eb txꞌok conobal chi yaoc ba yul in kꞌab, yuj in yakꞌon serbil, cꞌal yoc eb yin ayilal ayin yin camcꞌulal, ta man ok yetnej el eb in cꞌual xewilal, cax tecꞌan wal ok yut ba eb yin in trato,
Yuj tuꞌ xan chi yal eb ayin: Nabacꞌal chon oc yin cꞌajbancꞌulal, palta cꞌam chon elaꞌ. Nabacꞌal chi jiay co ba, palta cꞌam jelapnok yul a sat, ẍi eb. Yel toni, yujtol a yet cꞌual cꞌajbancꞌulal, yelcꞌulal che yun tzet chi cha e cꞌul, cꞌal e yetnen eb anima chi mulnaj ayex.
Masanil eb anima bay yulyibankꞌinal bay yichcan, masantacꞌal bay yayubcꞌu, caw wal miman yelapnok Jehová yul sat eb, yet ok yilon oc eb yin is maykꞌakꞌal. Yujtol ok jay Cham, axca wal junok elom aej tol chi xulaytek yuj cakxuchum cakꞌekꞌ.
Axa ayex tiꞌ ok e yik sacerdote yet Jehová yuj eb, chekbej ex Cham co Diosal. Ok tzalojbok e cꞌul yetok is beyomal juntzanxa nacionlak, watxꞌxacꞌal e yili yuj tzet yetal watxꞌ yili ay bay eb.
Lajwi tuꞌ, max naontek eb conob juntzan tzet max uj yettaxcꞌal payxa, yul tiempoal Moisés is chekbej Jehová. Xan max kꞌanlej ecꞌ eb: ¿Baytal ay Jehová tinaniꞌ, Cham max on colon el bay aꞌ mar, yetok eb jilomal? ¿Baytal ay Cham max yaoc is Yespíritu tol Asanxanej ocok co nan co xol?
Caw wal ok nojil bay jobeal yet Sarón yuj calnel, cꞌal bay jobeal yet Acor, ok low no wacax, a ton bay is jobbejal noꞌ jun conob ok oc ayilal ayin.
A wal yet ok e yilon juntzan tiꞌ, toxacꞌal ok tzalojbok aj e cꞌul. Ok akꞌlay yip e mimanil junelxa, axca chi yun yaxbi aj an acꞌun. Yujtol ok txꞌox wal Jehová is yipalil xol eb is chekbej, axa yowal cꞌul ok txꞌox xol eb ajcꞌul oc yin.
A ton jun yailal tiꞌ ok waoc yiban in conob yuj max quin is bekcan eb, yujtol max oc eb yin ayilal, cꞌal yakꞌon tzꞌa eb incienso bay comon dios tol a wal caw eb max watxꞌnen ajok.
Tol co mam ach, ẍi wal eb bay junok te teꞌ, cax chi yalon cꞌapax bay junok chꞌen chꞌen: Tol co txutx ach, ẍi wal eb. Axa pax ayin xin, a wal yichin eb chi yacbajcantek. Cꞌamxa wal chi tit tꞌanan eb jabok win. Axa wal yet chi yilon eb tol ay tzet ok onok: Sebach, colwajan, ẍinaj pax eb ayin.
Ex aj conob Israel, max in nabalnej el ex in chaon axca wal wuninal, cax chi wakꞌon jun txꞌotxꞌ caw wal ochebil ayex. Asannej oc jun txꞌotxꞌ tuꞌ caw wal watxꞌ yili bay yulyibankꞌinal tiꞌ. Max in naꞌ tol ok in e yaloc e mamok yin junelnej, tol manxa ok ex el in cꞌatan waloni.
Chi yal Jehová: A in conob, caw wal cꞌam is nabal, cꞌam chin yojtaknej elok. Lajan eb axca unin tol cꞌam jabok is nabal, cꞌam jabok chi nachaj el yuj eb. Caw wal jelan eb yin yunen yobtakilal, palta man yojtakok eb chi yun pax watxꞌil, ẍi Cham.
Abek juntzan tiꞌ ex conob tol cꞌam e nabal. Ay e sat, palta cꞌam chi jeꞌ e yiloni. Ay e txiquin, palta cꞌam chi jeꞌ e yabeni.
Yuj tuꞌ xan chi wal axca tiꞌ: Abek xin ex nacionlak, ojtaknejek el tzet ok on in conob tiꞌ.
Ilab tol a eb uninalej chi sayontek te siꞌ, axa eb mamej chi nubon oc kꞌakꞌej, axa eb txutxej chi watxꞌnen ixim cꞌoxox yet chi yakꞌ eb bay is diosal, xal chi yik yajawilal satcan. Caw wal chin is txꞌem eb, mawal axca yet chi yakꞌon eb vino bay txꞌok diosal.
A wal caw Jehová chi aloni: Ok wiel eb caytiꞌ, yujtol axca wal jun txꞌanil uva, ma jun teal higo cꞌam junok sat, toltax is xak lanan takilok, caytuꞌ yayji eb. Yuj wal tuꞌ xan a tzet max wakꞌ bay eb ok can yul kꞌab juntzan txꞌok conobal, ẍi Cham.
A camich mayal octok yulak co na, mayal apni oc yulak co despacho. Chi cam eb unin bay yulak calle, cꞌal eb achꞌej chi cam eb bay txonbal.
Akꞌon cuenta axca wal yayji oc a tojolal, cax manokab yetok yowal a cꞌul, talaj chon akꞌ lajwok ayok.
Max yal Jehová ayin: Tatol cꞌam chach tzakay akꞌon anej yetok eb chi beyi, ¿tzet wal ok yun a lajlen a bey yetok eb tol yiban chej ay ajok? Tatol chach telcꞌoj bay acꞌal watxꞌ yeqꞌui, ¿tzetto wal ok yun ecꞌ xolak pimal acꞌun bay tilak aꞌ Jordán?
Max yal Jehová bay Jeremías: Al bay a reyal, cꞌal bay is txutx: Ayanektek bay e trono cax chex ay chotan bay sat txꞌotxꞌ, yujtol ok ilay el e corona manxa watxꞌilok yin e jolom.
Mamin, ti wal chi co natek co yobtakil on xin, yetokcꞌal is yecꞌnakilal eb jichmam on. Caw wal max oc co mul on ayach.
Ok cam eb icham anima cꞌal eb unin bay jun conob tiꞌ; cꞌam mactxel ok mukon eb, cꞌam mactxel ok okꞌ yuj eb, tamwal ay mac ok txꞌoxil is cuscꞌulal yin yakꞌon yasjok is mimanil, cꞌal tzuklen el xil jolom.
Chi yal eb anima ayin axca tiꞌ: ¿Tzetlaj yayji is kꞌanej Jehová max yal jin tuꞌ? ¡Yunokab tzet chi yal tuꞌ tinaniꞌ xin! ẍi eb.
Max yalon eb conob axca tiꞌ: Co naek tzet watxꞌ ok jun yetok jun Jeremías tiꞌ. Aycꞌaltaꞌ sacerdote ok on cuyonok, aycꞌaltaꞌ eb aj nabal ok akꞌon co nabal, aycꞌaltaꞌ eb chekbej ok alon is kꞌanej Dios ayon. Yuj tuꞌ co tzꞌakek aj kꞌanej yiban, cax chi makꞌlay camok. Cꞌam chi jikej jabok tzet yetal chi yal tuꞌ, ẍi eb.
Ta chi walaꞌ tol cꞌamxa chach wakꞌ binajok, majxacꞌal walil a kꞌanej junelokxa, ta quin chi; axa chi yunej, axcaxa kꞌakꞌ chi yut ba a kꞌanej win. Toxcꞌa chi tzꞌatok in bakil yuj, chi wabej. Chi wochej chin mitxꞌ waay in ba walon a kꞌanej tuꞌ, palta cꞌamxa chi techaj wuj.
A despacho eb rey bay Judá, lajan yayji yul in sat axca watxꞌilal yili txꞌotxꞌ Galaad, axca cꞌapax jolom witz Líbano. Palta chi walaꞌ tol tzꞌinan txꞌotxꞌ ok wutcantok. Cꞌamxa junok mactxel ok cajay bay jun despacho tiꞌ.
Ayin Jehová in chi wal axca tiꞌ: Ok apnok jun cꞌual yet ok waon oc jun yinatil David tojol is nabal, yin reyal bay in conob. Ok yakꞌ wal reyal yin aj nabalil, cax yin wal tojolal ok yun beycꞌulnen el masanil conoblak.
Palta cꞌam chi jeꞌ yalon junok belan kꞌanej Is chekbanil Jehová; yujtol ta chi yal jun belan kꞌanej tuꞌ, a is kꞌanej tuꞌ chi meltzojcan oc yin ikatzil bay. Yujtol max yetnejtok eb anima tiꞌ tzet chi walaꞌ, ayin Dios iquis in tiꞌ, Jehová Yajaw in yin Masanil, e Diosal in cꞌapaxok.
A yet ok yuqꞌuen eb, ok xab eb yuj, cꞌal yoc eb yin yaxcꞌayinakil yuj, yujcꞌal jun owal ok watok xol eb tuꞌ, ẍi Cham.
A eb sacerdote, eb chi yaloc ba chekbejok Dios, cꞌal masanil eb conob, max yab wal eb yalon el cham Jeremías juntzan kꞌanej tuꞌ bay templo.
Xan max in cayicꞌnej walon juntzan tiꞌ bay Sedequías reyal Judá. Max cam wal walon bay: Aoc a ba yalan yikbej reyal Babilonia, yetokcꞌal is conob cham, yet watxꞌ cꞌam chex cami.
A cham Jeremías is chekbej Dios, max yatok jun carta bay eb yicham winakil conob iquisto ecꞌok, cꞌal bay eb sacerdote, cꞌal eb chekbej Dios, yetok bay masanil anima aj Jerusalén ibiltok yuj Nabucodonosor bay Babilonia.
Kꞌanlejekto wali ta ay junok winak chi yakꞌ aljok el unin. ¿Tzet yuj xan tol toxacꞌal lacan oc kꞌab eb winak caw wal tecꞌan yin is cꞌul chi wilaꞌ, axcaxacꞌal tol unin ok aljok? ¿Tzet yuj xan tol sakxacꞌal yili sat eb masanil?
Ok jay eb, cax ok bitnen eb bit bay tzalan yet Sión; ok yakꞌ tzalojbok eb cꞌul yuj jantak in watxꞌcꞌulalil, a ton trigo, vino, aceite, no calnel, cꞌal no wacax ok wakꞌ bay eb. Lajanxacꞌal ok yun eb axca wal junok awoj tol aycꞌal oc yal; manxa ok pax yip eb junelxa.
A ton yet tuꞌ lanan yakꞌwi owal eb is soldado Nabucodonosor yin Jerusalén. Axa pax Jeremías xin, ayicꞌ yin presoal bay amakꞌ, bay ayicꞌ eb taynemal is despacho eb reyal Judá.
A eb et israelal cꞌal eb aj Judá caw wal chi txꞌemtek eb yowal in cꞌul yuj jantakxa yobtakilal chi el yunen eb, lajanxacꞌal chi yun eb yetok eb is reyal, eb yajaw, eb sacerdote, cꞌal yetok eb in chekbej, cꞌal masanil anima cajan bay Jerusalén, cꞌal bay Judá.
Man ok cꞌay cꞌapax el eb sacerdote yetokcꞌal juntzanxa eb yinatil Leví; a eb tuꞌ ok akꞌon tzꞌa xajanbal ayin. Yin junjun cꞌu ok yakꞌon tzꞌa eb ixim trigo yin xajanbalil, cꞌal yakꞌon eb juntzanxa xajanbal ayin, ẍi Cham.
A yet ayoc Joacim cꞌajol Josías reyal bay Judá, a yet tuꞌ max kꞌanjab Jehová ayin, max yalon axca tiꞌ:
cax max toj bay is despacho cham rey, bay is cuarto cham ajtzꞌib, bay wajan ecꞌ eb cham caw wal mimek yopiso: a ton Elisama cham ajtzꞌib, Delaía is cꞌajol Semaías; Elnatán, is cꞌajol Acbor; Gemarías is cꞌajol Safán; Sedequías, is cꞌajol Hananías, cꞌal yetok juntzanxa eb ayoc yin yikbej tuꞌ.
A yet tuꞌ cꞌamto chi alay oc Jeremías preso, xan chito ecꞌjab xol conob.
Cax max takꞌwi cham rey Sedequías axca tiꞌ:
Cax max takꞌwi Sedequías bay cham Jeremías axca tiꞌ:
Yuj tuꞌ max toj il-lay Gedalías yuj eb bay Mizpa, a ton eb tiꞌ, Ismael, cꞌajol Netanías; Johanán cꞌal Jonatán cꞌajol Carea eb, yetok Seraías, cꞌajol Tanhumet, jaywan eb cꞌajol Efai, aj Netofa, yetok Jezanías, is cꞌajol jun winak aj Maacat, cꞌal yetok is soldado eb.
Palta a Ismael, yetok waxakwan eb ajun yetok max el eb, max tojcan eb bay conob Amón.
axa Azarías cꞌajol Osaías, Johanán cꞌajol Carea, yetokcꞌal juntzanxa winak tol caw wal chꞌaan, max yalon eb bay Jeremías: ¡Lekꞌtial juntzan kꞌanej chal tuꞌ! Yujtol a Jehová co Diosal maj yal ayach tol cꞌam chon toj cajan bay Egipto.
Max yalon cꞌapax eb xal ix:
Max kꞌanjab Jehová bay Jeremías yin tzet ok yun toj yakꞌon Nabucodonosor owal yin Egipto:
Caw wal chi okꞌ eb, chi el yal sat eb, chi ajtok bay witzal Luhit. Axa eb chi aytok bay Horonaim, caw wal chi el yaw eb yuj yailal tzet chi uji.
Ayin wal caw Jehová in chi walaꞌ: A bay Moab ok wakꞌ lajwok ayilal yin yakꞌon eb xajanbal bay juntzan lugar can ayajok, cꞌal yin yakꞌon tzꞌa eb incienso bay is diosal.
Ex aj Edom, yelxacꞌal yaynakil ok ex wut yintak masanil conob, cꞌamxa e yelapnok yul sat masanil anima.
Max yalon Jehová axca tiꞌ: A yet yajtok tuꞌ, a eb aj israel, cꞌal eb aj Judá, ok okꞌ eb, cax ok yaon oc ba eb yul in kꞌab.
Palta ayin Jehová, Yajaw in yin Masanil, ok in colcan el eb. Ok in beycꞌulnej el eb yin tojolal. Ok wakꞌon juncꞌulal bay in conob tiꞌ, axa bay conob Babilonia xin, asanxanej xiwcꞌulal ok watok yiban, ẍi Jehová.
A juntzan tzet yetal tuꞌ, cꞌam jabok yelapnok. Moj tol buchbejal yayji. A yet ok jay cꞌual, ok yakꞌ lajwok ay Jehová.
Ok aycꞌay Babilonia yuj jantakxa anima max yakꞌ cam bay Israel, cꞌal yuj jantakxa anima max yakꞌ cam bay yulyibankꞌinal, ẍi Cham.
Aꞌ max ul yakꞌon tzꞌa templo, yetok despacho eb rey, cꞌal yetok is na eb mimek winak bay conob tuꞌ.
Caw wal miman txequel yayji is yobtakil eb cajyom bay Jerusalén tuꞌ, palta tokwal ay tzet chi na eb yuj tzet ok jayoc yiban. Caw wal cꞌayubtakxacꞌal max yun yaycꞌay is conob eb, tok ay mactxel chi mimancꞌulnen eb. Chi yal eb anima bay tuꞌ: Mamin Jehová, ilawal co yailal on, yujtol a eb jajcꞌul on, mayal on yuch lajwok eb, ẍi eb.
Mayal yun tzet yetal nabil yuj Jehová, mayal wal yun is kꞌanej albil yuj yettaxcꞌal payxa. Max on yakꞌ lajwok yin cꞌamxacꞌal yabencꞌulal. Max el wal yin cꞌul yakꞌon tzewok eb ajcꞌul jin, max yion wal aj can yikbej eb ajcꞌul tuꞌ.
Caw wal watxꞌ Jehová yetok eb tol a Cham chi yaoc yipok cꞌul, a ton eb tol chi bekcꞌal oc ba yul kꞌab.
Mamin Jehová, max in awji ayach tacꞌal bay najatil yich jun olan tuꞌ.
A mactxel chon ukteni, yelxacꞌal jelan bey eb yintak no txꞌacbaj chi ecꞌ jenenok bay satcan. Tzakancꞌal eb jintak bay jolomlak witz; chon maklay yuj eb bay tzꞌinan txꞌotxꞌ.
Tojolcꞌal yayji is xub, axa yakan, ay yiskꞌak axca yet no wacax, cax chi jopopi axca chꞌen bronce tol caw wal watxꞌ niklay el tzꞌilal.
Cax max wilon jun kꞌabej batxantek ayin, ibil aj jun chulan un yuj.
Max yalon cꞌapax Cham ayin axca tiꞌ: A tinaniꞌ ach anima, iaj junok txꞌotxꞌ xan, cax chaon ay a satak, cax cha tzꞌiben ay yechel conob Jerusalén yin.
Ayin wal caw Jehová in chi walaꞌ, tol cꞌamxa mactxel ok wakꞌcan bay Jerusalén, masanilxacꞌal anima ok ecꞌ bay is cawilal, yobxacꞌal ok yal eb yin.
A mactxel mayal txon is txꞌotxꞌ, manxa ok jeꞌ yion paxok, yakꞌban iquisto ecꞌok yetok jun max manon tuꞌ, yujtol manxa ok jeꞌ tenlay oc wanaj jun yailal lanan jayocok. A eb yobtakwom, cꞌam junok eb ok jeꞌ colon ba.
Axca tu xin, max in yiontok bay puertail templo Jehová, a ton jun chi cancan bay yetcꞌulal norte. A bay tuꞌ chotan ay juntzan eb xal ix; lanan yokꞌ eb xal yuj is diosal chi yik Tamuz.
A eb querubín tuꞌ, canebcꞌal sat junjun. A jun is babel sat lajan wal axca sat junok querube; axa jun yet is cab, lajan axca sat anima; axa jun yet is yox, lajan wal yili axca sat no coj; axa jun yet is can, lajan wal yili axca sat no águila.
A pax eb tol oktocꞌal beybalnen juntzan beybalej tol yajbejtak yoc tu xin, ayin wal caw Jehová in chi walaꞌ, tol ok waoc yailal yiban eb yuj, ẍi Jehová, cachi, ẍi Cham ayin.
Max kꞌanjab Jehová ayin, max yalon axca tiꞌ:
Axca tu xin, ok wakꞌ meltzoj is nabal eb israel ayin, a ton eb pojnak el ba wintak yujcꞌal is comon dios.
A yet cꞌual max alji, maj cꞌuplay el is muxuc, maj achinelayok, tamwal max alay oc atzꞌam yin, maj cꞌapax pichlayok.
Yuj tuꞌ xan txꞌok yel ix yintak juntzanxa ajmul ix. Cꞌam mac chi sayon ecꞌok yet chi mulji yetok, tamwal chi tojlanej eb, palta tol a ix chi tojlanej mac chi oc yin ajmulal yetok, yuj tuꞌ xan txꞌok yel yintak juntzanxa eb ajmul ix.
Max kꞌanjab Jehová ayin, max yalon axca tiꞌ:
Cꞌam chi oc yetok eb chi chaon kꞌin bay jolomlak witz yet chi oc eb ayilal bay yechelej. Cꞌam chi yaoc eb is lekꞌti diosal eb yet israelal tuꞌ yipok cꞌul. Cꞌam chi mulji yetok yistzil yet animail, cax cꞌam chi junanej ba yetok yistzil yet ayoc ix yin is bisbal xajaw.
Max yab wal juntzan nacionlak is kꞌumal tzet wal chi yunej. Max mitxꞌlay yuj eb yul junok yal, yetok gancho max jutxtok eb, masantacꞌal max apni oc bay Egipto.
Mimanokab wal yelapnok jun cꞌual xewilal tol wet yayji oc yul sat eb. A jun tuꞌ tol yechelej yayji yin jun trato max in watxꞌnej yetok eb. Caywal tuꞌ ok yun yojtaknen el eb tol ayin ton Jehová is Diosal in eb.
Ach anima, meltzojantok acan bay yetcꞌulal Jerusalén, cax chach kꞌanjabtok yin templo. Alcan el in kꞌanej yin conob Israel.
Axca wal junok bolob, caywal tuꞌ ok wut wion el yowal in cꞌul e yin; ok ex waoc yul kꞌab eb anima yob is nabal, cꞌal jelan yin yakꞌon lajwok.
A eb anima asanxanej yin yetnen yet animail chi yunej, cꞌal yin elkꞌan. A wal eb mebaꞌ, eb cꞌam tzet ay, a eb chi yetnej eb. Yelxacꞌal man tojolok tzet chi yun eb yin eb txꞌok conobal.
A ton wal juntzan tiꞌ chi wal ayin Jehová Yajaw in tiꞌ: Ayin ok ach waoc yul kꞌab juntzan nación tol yob a cꞌul yin, a ton juntzan tol yajbil oj.
Ok cancꞌal can juntzan chicꞌ tuꞌ bay yiban jun chꞌen tuꞌ wuj, yet watxꞌ txequelcꞌal yayji, xan chi titcꞌal yowal in cꞌul cax chin paktzejcꞌal.
Cax ok waon oc yailal yiban Moab. Caywal tuꞌ ok yun nachaj el yuj eb tol ayin ton Jehová in.
Max kꞌanjab Jehová ayin max yaloni:
A eb chi makꞌom bey juntzanxa te barco, chi aytek eb yul is barco tuꞌ. A eb chi ion bey teꞌ tuꞌ, chi oc waan eb ti aꞌ mar.
Ach anima, meltzojantok acan bay yetcꞌulal conob Sidón cax chalon el in kꞌanej yin.
Max kꞌanjab Jehová ayin, max yaloni:
Lajan ach wal yetok junok qꞌuisis, ma axca junok te cꞌuteꞌ ay bay Líbano, a kꞌablak teꞌ, xiwil watxꞌil yenel bay kꞌaktelak, caw wal can ayajok, cax chi ecꞌtacꞌal aj tel yiban juntzanxa teꞌ.
Ayin caw Jehová in chi walaꞌ tol caytuꞌ ok yun sakbok el aꞌ aej, melelixacꞌal ok yun bey aꞌ.
Ach anima, al bay eb et conob axca tiꞌ: Ta ay junok winak watxꞌ is beybal cax chi oc is mul, man ok colchaj yuj is watxꞌ beybalil yet yalantok tuꞌ. Ta ay cꞌapax junok winak yelxacꞌal yob is beybal, cax chi naon ba cꞌul cax chi yunen watxꞌil, man ok cam yuj is yobtakil yet yalantok. Axa pax junok watxꞌ is beybal xin, cax chi oc pax is mul, a is watxꞌ beybalil yet yalantok tuꞌ, cꞌamxa yelapnok yet chi iquisbicꞌal ecꞌok.
Yuj tu xin, ex yilomal in conob, abek wal juntzan kꞌanej tiꞌ.
Tzꞌininixacꞌal ok wutcantok siquilal txꞌotxꞌ Seir, ok wakꞌ cam mactxel chi ecꞌ bay tuꞌ.
Yuj tu xin, al bay eb et conob Israel: Axca wal tiꞌ yalon Jehová Cham Yajaw: A tzet ok wunej, man e yujok ayex israel ex tiꞌ ok wunej, palta a wuj ayin tiꞌ, yujtol e yuj xan yob max yun in binaj xol juntzan nacionlak bay max quex apni oc tuꞌ.
Ayin caw chi walaꞌ tol ok waoc Wespíritu e yin, axa e yiquisbi ecꞌ tuꞌ; axa ex wakꞌon cajay ecꞌ junelxa bay e txꞌotxꞌ tuꞌ. Axca tuꞌ ok yun e yojtaknen elok tol ayin ton Jehová in. A tzet chi wal tiꞌ ok wakꞌ yunej, ẍi Jehová, cachi, ẍi Cham yin tzet max yakꞌ wil tuꞌ.
cay wal tuꞌ ok yun oc yin akꞌon owal yin in conob Israel. Ach Gog, toxacꞌal ok makay el sat txꞌotxꞌ txꞌotxꞌ oj axca asun. A yet juntzan lajub cꞌual tuꞌ, ok ach watek yin jun in txꞌotxꞌ tiꞌ. Ojcꞌal wal ach tiꞌ, xan ok in yojtaknej el juntzanxa nación, yet ok in txꞌoxon in mimanbilal satak eb.
Masanil juntzanxa nación ok yojtaknej elok tol a eb israel max toj eb yin presoal yujcꞌal is yobtakil, yujtol caw wal tenomtak max yut ba eb ayin, xan max in el txꞌuman bay eb, max in bekoncan eb bay eb ajcꞌul, axca tuꞌ max yun yaycꞌay eb, cꞌal makꞌlay cam eb bay xol owal.
A jun na tuꞌ, yetokcꞌal is tentail, aycꞌal is wentenail axcacꞌal juntzanxa tuꞌ. A yechel yin masanil, ay 25 metro is kꞌatil, yetok nan yoxlajoneb metro is sat.
A juntzan cuarto ayoc yinlak tuꞌ, a juntzan ay bay yet is cab piso, miman yul yintak juntzan ay bay babel piso. Axa juntzan bay yox piso, miman yul yintak juntzan bay is cab piso. Ay jun kꞌoch be chi toj bay babel piso, chi ecꞌaj bay is cab piso, masantacꞌal chi ajapnok bay yet yox piso.
Lajancꞌal cawxi, lajancꞌal yechel axca wal juntzan cuartolak bay yetcꞌulal norte. Lajancꞌal yayji bay chon oqui cꞌal bay chon eli, yetokcꞌal jun jakan nan yul.
Chi lajwi tuꞌ, cax ok yion aj eb no wacax max akꞌlay yin xajanbalil tuꞌ, cax ok yakꞌon tzꞌa eb noꞌ bay yinel templo bay jun lugar txequel yayji.
Acꞌalaꞌ ta ay bay chi oc owal, a eb chi beycꞌulnen elok atacꞌalaꞌ yalon in ley. Chi yiken eb leyalil juntzan in kꞌin, cax chi yiken eb jun cꞌual xewilal tol wet yayji ocok.
A yet junjun cꞌu yin ukeb cꞌual kꞌin tuꞌ, yowalil chi yakꞌ jun yajaw tuꞌ ukcꞌon no achꞌej wacax, cꞌal ukcꞌon no icham calnel, a ton wal noꞌ tol cꞌam jabok is tacnakilal. Chi akꞌlay tzꞌa noꞌ yin xajanbalil ayin. Yetok cꞌapax noꞌ tuꞌ, chi akꞌlay junok noꞌ mam chiwo yin xajanbalil yuj yakꞌlay tan yobtakilal.
Lajwi tuꞌ max yechen pax junxa 500 metro cax max in yion pax ecꞌtok bay yul aꞌ aej; axa yet tuꞌ max ajapnok aꞌ bay jolom in penec. Max yechen pax junxa 500 metro, cax max in yion pax ecꞌtok bay yul aꞌ aej. Axa yet tuꞌ, max ajapnok aꞌ aej tuꞌ bay in nan.
A jun makan txꞌotxꞌ txꞌotxꞌ wet yayji oc tuꞌ, ay nan is yoxlajoneb kilómetro is tel, yetok lajoneb kilómetro is sat.
Palta max naꞌ Daniel tol cꞌam chi can yin yobal satak Dios yuj is lobej cꞌal is yucꞌaꞌ cham rey tuꞌ, xan max kꞌan bay cham Aspenaz tuꞌ tol cꞌam chi akꞌlay pural yet chi loꞌ juntzan loj tuꞌ.
