Yakꞌban lanan elon jun tiꞌ mamin rey, axa bay sat jun witz, tocꞌal max tit jun chꞌen chꞌen tol cꞌamcꞌal mac max tenontek. Palancꞌal jayoc yin yakan jun yechelej tuꞌ bay soman hierro yetok txꞌotxꞌ.
cax max kꞌanlen el cham rey bay eb axca tiꞌ:
Cax max jayoc masanil eb tzꞌakan cꞌul, eb aj bal, cꞌal eb chi nachaj el yuj tzetbil yayji oc waycan, cꞌal eb naom el kꞌanej, cax max walon in wayich tuꞌ bay eb, palta maj wal jeꞌ yuj eb yalon ayin tzet wal yelapnok.
Yet max lajwi tiempoal yailal ayoc wiban, ayin Nabucodonosor in tiꞌ, max in aj tꞌanan bay satcan cax max watxꞌji el in nabal yin in yaxcꞌayinakcꞌulal. Max walon watxꞌ kꞌanej yin Cham Axacꞌal Ocok, axa wion aj can Cham tol aycꞌal ecꞌ yin tojbalkꞌinal:
Axa max yun xin, yelxacꞌal chꞌaan max ot a ba satak Cham Yajawil satcan. Max akꞌon ilaytek bay a meẍa juntzan copa cꞌal juntzan secꞌ yet is templo Cham. A yul juntzan tuꞌ max ocꞌ an vino yetok masanil eb awtebil oj, cax max e yion aj can juntzan dios tol oro, plata, hierro, teꞌ cꞌal chꞌen, a ton juntzan dios tol cꞌam chi jeꞌ yiloni, cꞌam chi jeꞌ yabeni, tamwal ay jabok tzet yetal yojtak. Cax manak bay Dios max al watxꞌ kꞌanej, ti pax wal a yul kꞌab Cham ay a cawil, cax a cꞌapax Cham chi naon tzet chonej.
—Matawal ok ach col-lay yuj a Diosal tol ayachcꞌal oc yin akꞌon serbil, ẍi cham.
Cax max akꞌlay is yikbej cꞌal is mimanbilal yin reyal. Masanil nacionlak cꞌal tiejlak chi akꞌon serbil. A is yipalil aycꞌal yin tojbalkꞌinal, cꞌam yechel ok lajwok is yikbej.
Ayin Daniel in tiꞌ, lanan in naon yin tzet max wil tuꞌ, yet chi nachaj el wuj tzet wal yelapnok; axa max yunej, max txꞌoxon aj ba in satak jun axca wal yili anima,
Jojtak Mamin tol choncꞌal tzet chalaꞌ. Yuj tuꞌ elok wal yin a cꞌul eon el yailal, cꞌal yowal a cꞌul ayoc yiban conob Jerusalén, yujtol a conob yayji, cꞌal et yayji jun tzalan Sión. Masanil wal nacionlak ay cawilal chi buchwaj eb yin a conob Jerusalén, yujcꞌal wal co yobtakil on, cꞌal yuj is yobtakil eb jichmam on.
¿Tzet wal ok yun in kꞌanjab ayin a chekbej in tiꞌ etok, Mamin? Tutun wal cꞌamxa wip, cax cꞌamxa chi wi in cakꞌekꞌ chi wabej, quin chi.
Ok yaoc is yipalil yipok cꞌul, cax ok yakꞌon owal yin reyal sur yetok jun miman bulan is soldado, palta yin cꞌapax ipejal ok takꞌwok reyal sur tuꞌ, cax ok oc yakꞌon owal yetok jun miman bulan soldado caw wal ay yipalil tuꞌ, palta majxa jeꞌ tecꞌban ba eb is soldado tuꞌ yujtol ok ilay aytek sat reyal sur.
Axa takꞌwi ayin tuꞌ: Cꞌamtocꞌal cha na yin juntzan tiꞌ Daniel, yujtol a masanil juntzan tzet yetal tiꞌ, tocꞌal ok cꞌuaycan ecꞌok masantacꞌal yet lajubal.
Ok wakꞌon pax is yuva junelxa. A jobeal Acor manxa jobealok bilcꞌulal ok yunej; palta axcaxa junok beal yipcꞌulalil ok wutcanok. A bay tuꞌ ok takꞌwok ayin, axca wal max yun yet kꞌopojto, axca yet jun cꞌual yet max eltek bay Egipto.
