a yet lanan wanten in conob Efraín, cꞌal Samaria, a yet tuꞌ max txecloj aj is yajbejtakil, cꞌal is yobtakilal eb. Yujtol junlajanxacꞌal chi yun beybalnen eb lekꞌtial. Elkꞌomxacꞌal el eb masanil. Tojolxacꞌal yoc yulak na. A bay yulak calle chi elkꞌan eb yinlak anima.
Manchak ex tzaloj ex israel, manchak ex aj tꞌuknaj yuj tzalojcꞌulal axca eb txꞌok conobal, yujtol max e bekcan e Diosal, axca chi yun bekoncan eb ajmul ix yichamil. Caw wal chex tzaloj e txꞌoxon e camcꞌulal bay Baal, yujtol watxꞌ chi yun sat e yawoj yuj e yaloni.
