Chito ajcꞌal can yaon oc is mul. Chi watxꞌnej aj chꞌen plata is diosalok, axca wal chi yochej cꞌul, cꞌal axca wal chi tit yin is nabal eb watxꞌnem yechelej. Chi lajwi tuꞌ chi yalon aj paxok: Akꞌek e xajanbal bay, ẍi. Axa eb anima xin, chi tzꞌubil eb tiꞌ jun yechelej lajan yili axca wacax tuꞌ.
Mayal yetnejtok noꞌ an uva, mayal yakꞌ cꞌapax lajwok el noꞌ te higo. Tzꞌininixacꞌal max yuncan yuj noꞌ. Max yion cꞌapax el noꞌ is tzꞌumal masanil awoj tuꞌ, sakxacꞌal max yun yilican is kꞌablak.
Okꞌokab eb sacerdote, eb chi akꞌon serbil Jehová. A bay nan xol templo yetok altar, yalokab eb axca tiꞌ: Akꞌ mimancꞌulal jiban ayon a conob on tiꞌ, Mamin Jehová. Cꞌamokab mactxel chon buchoni. Cꞌamokab chon aycꞌay yul kꞌab eb txꞌok conobal, cax cꞌamokab chi yal eb axca tiꞌ: ¿Baytal ay e Diosal tuꞌ? manokab ẍiok eb, ẍiokab eb sacerdote.
Manxa animaok bay jobeal bay ok oc beycꞌulal, toxa ok txꞌox ba cꞌual yet yowal cꞌul Jehová bay tuꞌ.
Chi yal Jehová: Ayin Jehová in chi walaꞌ, tol max wakꞌ lajwok eb amorreo, yuj wakꞌon is txꞌotxꞌ eb ayex. Junelnej max wakꞌ lajwok eb, caxcꞌal mimek tel eb axca tel te cꞌuteꞌ, cax caw eb axca te jiꞌ.
A jun cab conobal ex bay cꞌam chi yakꞌ nab, max ex toj sayoj aej bay junxa conob bay chi yakꞌ nab; palta maj yab aꞌ yet chi ecꞌtok e takintial. Tokwal yuj tuꞌ max ex meltzojtek ayin.
A wal ayex tiꞌ ex israel, a yin cawinak abil max ex ecꞌ bay txꞌotxꞌ takin txꞌotxꞌ. Tokwal a ayin max e yakꞌ tzꞌa xajanbal, cꞌal ofrenda bay tuꞌ.
—¿Tzet yetal chel tuꞌ Amós? ẍi Cham.
A wal eb ix kꞌopoj ix caw wal watxꞌ yili, cꞌal eb achꞌej caw wal tecꞌan, toxacꞌal ok pax yip eb yuj takintial yet jun cꞌual tuꞌ.
A yet max ilay eltek masanil is beyomal Jerusalén yuj eb ajcꞌul, a yet max makꞌlay poj is puertail jun conob tuꞌ yuj eb txꞌok conobal, ayex tiꞌ tocꞌal max ex oc tꞌananok. Yet max yaon oc eb ajcꞌul masanil tzetak yetal ay bay yin suerteal, cax max ilaytok is beyomal yuj eb, lajanxacꞌal max e yut e ba yetok eb ajcꞌul tuꞌ.
Yuj tu xin max tewi eb bay Jehová, max yalon eb axca tiꞌ: Mamin, manchak on akꞌ cam yuj is camichal jun winak tiꞌ, axca chi yun cam eb makꞌom cam anima, yujtol ach tiꞌ Jehová lanan onen tzet nabil oj, ẍi eb.
—¿Tom watxꞌxacꞌal chot a ba, yuj chi tit owal? ẍi Cham.
Yuj wal tuꞌ max yal Jehová axca tiꞌ: Ayin tiꞌ, ay wal tzet chin naꞌ cꞌapax e yin ayex tiꞌ. Ok watok junok miman yailal e xol, cꞌamxa tzet watxꞌ ok yun e colchaji. Tok okto e maynej e ba e yecꞌjabi, yujtol is cꞌualxa jun miman yailal.
A tinaniꞌ xin ex aj Jerusalén, ¿tzet yuj xan tol chi el e yaw axca ix ix yet chi ajapnok cꞌual watxꞌji cꞌul yuj yuneꞌ? ¿Tom yuj cꞌam junok rey bay ayex tiꞌ? ¿Ma yujtol cꞌamxa junok eb aom oc nabalej e xol?
¿Tzet ok yun wakꞌon mimancꞌulal yiban juntzan anima tiꞌ, tol a echbal man tzꞌakanok chi kꞌan eb?
Caw wal chi bilaj juntzan witz satak Cham, cax chi uljitok tzalanlak. A masanil txꞌotxꞌ txꞌotxꞌ tiꞌ, chi bilajok yet chi txꞌoxon ba Cham; chi luklon aj yulyibankꞌinal yetok masanil anima
A masanil mactxel ok ilon ocok, toxacꞌal ok el eb bay. Ok yalon eb axca tiꞌ: A wal Nínive, mayal lajwi ayok. ¿Macto wal ok okꞌ cꞌul yin? ¿Bayto wal ok yiꞌ mac ok mimancꞌulnenok? ẍi mi eb.
Axca yayji oc junok taynemal conob yin yopiso, caytuꞌ ok yun in taynen wabej tzet ok yal Cham Yajaw ayin, yet chi nachaj el wuj is paktzebal in kꞌanlebal bay, quin chi.
Axa cꞌu, yetok xajaw max oc wanajok, yet max el joplabok a julbal, cax max aj joplabok a lanza.
A wal ayex titnak ex bay Creta, mac ex tol cajan ex bay tilak aꞌ mar, mayal yal Jehová tzet yetal ok jayoc e yiban. Chi yal axca tiꞌ: Ok wakꞌ lajwok ay Canaán is txꞌotxꞌal eb filisteo; cꞌamxa junok mactxel ok cajaycan ecꞌ bay tuꞌ, ẍi Cham.
A wal yet jun cꞌual tuꞌ, ok wakꞌ yowalil bay juntzan eb max ex etneni. Ok in colwaj bay eb yatak ay, cꞌal bay eb sakleminak cantok. Ok wi wal aj can e mimanbilal baytakcꞌal max quex intaknelay elok.
Ilab yet ay mac max toj ion 20 echbal trigo yaloni, axa yet max apni bay cꞌuan, asanxanej 10 echbal ixim ayicꞌok. Ta ay cꞌapax mac max toj bay chi watxꞌji vino yet chi toj yiajtek junok 50 moc vino yaloni, axa yet max yion ajtek, asannej 20 moc max ajtek.
Yuj tu xin, max wilon toj jun ángel maxax kꞌanjab wetok tuꞌ; ay junxa ángel max eltek ul chaoni, aꞌ max alon bay:
Max in kꞌanlen pax bay: ¿Tzet chi yal elapnok cab te olivo, tol junjuncꞌal bay junjun is tzꞌeyil jun batxlub candil tuꞌ? quin chi bay.
A yet is can cꞌual waay yet is baloneb xajaw, (a ton xajaw chi yik Quisleu), yet is can abilxa yoc Darío yin reyal, a yet tuꞌ max kꞌanjab Jehová ayin Zacarías in tiꞌ.
A ton wal juntzan tiꞌ yowalil ok e yun ayex tiꞌ. Asancꞌal tzet yetal yel ok e yal-lej ayex junjun ex. Beycꞌulnejek yin tojolal, yet watxꞌ ay juncꞌulal e xol.
Ayin ok wakꞌ is tecꞌanil eb yinatil Judá, cax ok wakꞌon colchaj el eb yinatil José. Axa wikban meltzoj eb bay is conob junelxa tuꞌ, yujtol chi okꞌ in cꞌul yin eb. Cax ok can pax can eb junelxa, axca tol cꞌam bay max wiel eb yin in cꞌul. Ayin ton Jehová is Diosal in eb, tol chi wabcꞌal is txaj eb.
Palta ayin Jehová in tiꞌ, yin babelal ok in colcan el eb yinatil Judá, yet watxꞌ man ok maynej ba eb yinatil David, cꞌal yetok masanil eb cajan bay Jerusalén yintak eb aj Judá.
Acꞌal oc jun yailal max aycꞌay yiban eb anima, acꞌalaꞌ ok jay cꞌapax yiban no chej, no mula, no camello, no burro, cꞌal yiban masanil is jobbejal noꞌ eb ajcꞌul ayicꞌ bay is campamento eb.
¿Tom man junnejok co Mam xin, a ton Dios Cham max on watxꞌneni? ¿Tzet yuj xin xan chi jetnelej co ba, cax chi jakꞌlen yobcꞌulalil jin junjun on, cax chi jetnentok is trato Dios max watxꞌnej yetok eb jichmam?
Ilek wali, ok in chektok Elías in chekbej, yet cꞌamto chi apni oc jun cꞌual yet ok txecloj aj yowal in cꞌul; a wal jun cꞌual tuꞌ, miman yayji ocok, ayxa is may ok yunej.
—¿Baytal ay jun winak unin max alji, jun tol ok oc e reyalok ayex Israel ex tiꞌ? A bay chi ajol cꞌu, ata tuꞌ max jil yajol jun waycan, jun max txꞌoxon yaljubal jun unin tuꞌ ayon. Yuj tuꞌ xan max on tit ul jaon ay co ba bay, ẍi eb.
Axa eb aj Jerusalén, yetok eb aj Judea, cꞌal jantak eb cajan tilak aꞌ Jordán, chi bet eb abxalwok bay cham.
—Masanil juntzan chin txꞌoxtok ayach tiꞌ, ok wakꞌ ayach, ta chach ay jajan ayin, cax chalon a ba ayin, ẍi bay.
Tzalojanek sicꞌlibil, yujtol caw miman watxꞌilal ok e chaꞌ is paktzilok bay satcan. Axca wal chi yun e yilon yailal tiꞌ, cay wal tuꞌ max yun yilon eb chekbej Dios yailal yet payxa.
Tzancꞌal mactxel chi kꞌanon majanej junok tzet yetal ayex, akꞌek bay, cax manchak e basnej.
Palta ta ay ex txꞌok txꞌok bay che yaoc e sat xin, chex cancan xol kꞌekkꞌinal yuj. A e sakkꞌinalil tuꞌ, ta chi qꞌuexpoj oc yin kꞌekkꞌinalil, ok ex canxacꞌal xol kꞌekkꞌinal.
19-20 Yuj tu xin, a eb chi yaloc ba chekbejok Dios tuꞌ, ok e yojtaknej wal el eb sicꞌlibil yuj tzetak yetal chi el yunen eb. Masanil te teꞌ tol man watxꞌok sat chi yakꞌaꞌ, chi kꞌaklay aj teꞌ, cax chi kꞌoklaytok teꞌ xol kꞌakꞌej tzꞌaꞌok, cayton tuꞌ ok utlay eb man watxꞌok beybal.
Lajwi tu xin, axa yalon Jesús bay cham capitán tuꞌ axca tiꞌ:
—Ocanek yin noꞌ xin, ẍi bay eb.
Yetok cꞌapaxok, tok ay mactxel chi aon ay vino tolto chi watxꞌji, yulak icham tzꞌum netal vino. Yujtol a yet chi sipcꞌoj ajok, chi nicꞌchaj no tzꞌum tuꞌ yuj. Nabacꞌal chi etax el vino cꞌal no tzꞌum tuꞌ, xan a yul no acꞌ tzꞌum chi ay vino ato watxꞌji tuꞌ, yet watxꞌ cꞌamcꞌal junok tzet chi etax elok, ẍi Jesús bay eb.
A yet max yilon oc Jesús eb anima, max cus oc cꞌul yin eb, yujtol lajan yayji eb axca junok bulan calnel cꞌam yilomal. Ayoc eb yin somcꞌulal, cꞌal yin yatakilal max yilaꞌ.
A juntzan tzet chi wal ayex yin ewantakil, alek el masanil bay anima. Yetok juntzan tocꞌal chin saj e yabej, alek el yulak calle.
Ta che yochej che yaoc yin e cꞌul tzet chi wal tiꞌ, ok nachaj el e yuj, tol a Juan tuꞌ, a ton Elías echbanebil jayi.
Max takꞌwi Jesús bay eb:
A Dios ok ex beycꞌulnen yuj tzet che yalaꞌ. Ata ok alonok, ta ok oc tzet max e yal tuꞌ e mulok ma cꞌamak, ẍi Jesucristo.
Xan max takꞌwi Cham bay eb axca tiꞌ: Asan ayex chi txꞌox Dios juntzan tzet yetal cꞌamto mac ojtaknej, yet watxꞌ chi nachaj el e yuj tzet chi yun e yoc yul kꞌab Cham. Axa bay juntzanokxa xin, cꞌam chi akꞌlay yojtaknej el eb.
A txꞌotxꞌ txꞌotxꞌ bay max oc awoj tuꞌ, a yulyibankꞌinal tiꞌ chi yalaꞌ. A ixim inat watxꞌ tuꞌ, a ton eb ayxa oc yul kꞌab Cham aj satcan chi yalaꞌ. A an awal an, a ton eb yet diablo chi yalaꞌ.
Axa yet max chaon Herodes kꞌinal yabilal xin, max wajban oc anima. Axa canalwi ix yuneꞌ Herodías tuꞌ satak eb masanil. Caw wal watxꞌ yecꞌ ix max yil Herodes.
Axa yaytek Pedro yul te barco tuꞌ, cax max beytoj bay Jesús yiban aꞌ.
—Watxꞌ alnej el ayon tzet chi yal elapnok jun cuybanilej max al bay eb fariseo tuꞌ, ẍi bay Cham.
Catatuꞌ max yalon Jesús bay eb anima tuꞌ, tol chi ay chotan eb sat txꞌotxꞌ.
A ayach ok wakꞌ laweal yet chi oc anima yul kꞌab Cham aj satcan. A tzet ok akꞌ yowalil bay yulyibankꞌinal tiꞌ, a ton tzet ayxacꞌaltaꞌ yowalil yuj Cham aj satcan. Axa tzet man ok akꞌ yowalil bay yulyibankꞌinal tiꞌ, a ton tzet cꞌamcꞌaltaꞌ yowalil yuj Cham aj satcan, ẍi bay.
Palta chi wal ayex, tol ulnakxa ecꞌok; palta maj nachaj el yuj eb anima tatol aꞌ. Yuj tuꞌ xan max yakꞌ wal eb yochwan yin axca chi yochej. Caytuꞌ ok wut cꞌapax waben yail yuj eb, ayin Chekbilintek yuj Dios xol eb jet animail tiꞌ, ẍi bay eb is cuywom tuꞌ.
Tzancꞌal mac chi chaon junok unin axca jun tiꞌ, yuj wal tol wet, ayin chin is chaꞌ.
Ta cꞌam che yakꞌ cꞌapax mimancꞌulal yin masanil e cꞌul yin yobtakil e yet animail chi oc ayex, man ok yakꞌ cꞌapax mimancꞌulal co Mam Dios e yin, ẍi Jesús bay eb.
—Ta chochej wal tol chach tzꞌaknaj el eken masanil, txoncan el masanil tzet ay ayach, cax cha pojontok tojol tuꞌ xol eb mebaꞌ; catatu bian ok a chaon a beyomal bay satcan. Chi lajwi tu xin, cax chach ecꞌcꞌal cuywok wintak, ẍi Jesús bay.
A yet lanan yajtok Jesús yetok eb anima yul beal conob Jerusalén, max yawten el eb is lajcawan cuywom xol eb, max yalon bay eb axca tiꞌ:
Cayton tuꞌ max yun yion ba tzet tzꞌibbilcan yuj cham chekbej Dios yet payxa, yet max yaloncan axca tiꞌ:
—¿Tzet ekbej xan max on juntzan tuꞌ ewi? ¿Mac wal akꞌnej ekbej tuꞌ? ẍi eb bay.
A chꞌen chꞌen max yintaknej el eb watxꞌnem na, a chꞌen max oc yin jolom txiquin na. A jun tiꞌ max yun Cham Jajawil cax chi cꞌayaj co cꞌul yuj, ẍi yul txꞌan Un Tzꞌibbilcan tuꞌ.
—Akꞌek tzet yetal yetcꞌaltaꞌ cham yajaw tuꞌ bay xin, axa tzet yetal yetcꞌaltaꞌ Dios, akꞌek cꞌapax bay, ẍi bay eb.
Max lajwi tu xin, max yalon Jesús bay eb anima, cꞌal bay eb is cuywom axca tiꞌ:
A tzet max chail yich eb e yichmam tuꞌ yunen xin, a lanan e lajonxacꞌal canok.
Tewanek bay Dios tol manokab nabil kꞌinalok yet ok ex el tuꞌ, tamwal yet cꞌual xewilalokab cꞌapaxok.
A yet man naanok jay is patrón tuꞌ yuj, a ton yet tuꞌ ok jayok.
Yujtol a mac ay yet, ok akꞌlay tzꞌakil bay, yet watxꞌ chi aj can bay. Axa eb cꞌam wal yet, a jabok yet eb aytaꞌa, ok ilay ecꞌ bay eb.
—¿Tzet yuj xan che txꞌem cus cꞌul jun ix tiꞌ? A jun max yun ix ayin tiꞌ, caw watxꞌ.
Max lajwi bitnen eb jun bit chi bitnejcꞌaltaꞌ eb bay Dios, axa toj eb bay tzalan Olivo tuꞌ.
Palta ay jun ajun yetok Jesús, max tzacꞌajtek yespada yin aymanil. Max tzocꞌon el is txiquin jun is moso cham sat sacerdote.
Lananxa wal yeltok Pedro bay puertail amakꞌ tuꞌ, cax max il-lay yuj junxa ix, max yalon ix bay eb wajan ecꞌok:
Palta cꞌam junok belan kꞌanej max paktzej bay. Yuj tuꞌ xan caw max cꞌayaj cꞌul Pilato yin Cham.
Max lajwi tu, max yaon oc eb yin te curus, cax max yaon oc eb soldado suerte yin is pichil Cham, yuj pojoncan ecꞌ eb xol.
Chotan ay María aj Magdala yetok junxa María cawilal chꞌen chꞌen tuꞌ.
Yuj tu xin, asek cuywaj xolak anima bay junjun conob, yet watxꞌ ok oc eb in cuywomok. Che yakꞌcan bautizar eb yin bi Dios Mamej, yin in bi ayin Dios Cꞌajolej in tiꞌ, cꞌal yin bi Dios Espíritu Santo.
Max cꞌayaj cꞌul masanil anima max iloni. Yuj tuꞌ xan max cꞌoli yalubtanen eb:
Palta ay juntzan eb meẍtol yin ley Moisés chotan ecꞌ bay tuꞌ. Max naon eb axca tiꞌ:
—¿Tom cꞌamto bay che yil yul txꞌan Un Tzꞌibbilcanok, tzet max yun David junel, yet max tit is wajil yetok eb ajun yetok?
A yet max yaben eb yuẍtak Jesús, cꞌal is txutx, max tit eb; tꞌinanxa chi ul yitok eb, yujtol mayal oc Cham locoal yalon eb.
Axa yalon bay eb tuꞌ: Asan ayex chi txꞌox Dios juntzan tzet yetal tol cꞌamto mac ojtaknej, yet watxꞌ chi nachaj el e yuj tzet chi yun e yoc yul is kꞌab Cham. Palta a bay eb comon anima, asan juntzan abix txꞌoxom el cuybanilej chi wal bay eb,
Axa yaj wan Jesús, max tenon oc waan jun cakꞌekꞌ tuꞌ. Max yalon cꞌapax bay aꞌ mar:
Palta maj chaꞌ ajtok Cham nak yetok, max yalon bay nak axca tiꞌ:
Max oc mitxꞌan yin kꞌab ix, cax max yalon bay ix axca tiꞌ:
—Caw cꞌam leyal cha montej el yistzil oẍtak, ẍi bay.
—¿Chi mi toj co man 200 denario pan, chi yal tuꞌ, cax chi jakꞌon low eb? ẍi eb.
—Ayex tiꞌ caw wal cabsat ex. Yel ton taꞌ tzet albilcan yuj Isaías e yin, yet max tzꞌibencan axca tiꞌ yul txꞌan Un Tzꞌibbilcanok:
Yuj tuꞌ xan max yal Cham bay ix axca tiꞌ:
Axa yalubtanen eb cuywom tuꞌ yuj tzet max yal tuꞌ:
Max lajwi tu xin, max yawten eb is cuywom cꞌal yetok juntzanxa eb anima. Max yalon bay eb:
Tzancꞌal bay ayicꞌ nak cax chi titaꞌ, chi telcꞌoj nak yuj. Chi eltek sukuwal tiꞌ nak yuj, cax chi natxꞌatxꞌi ye nak. Caw lanan bakbi nak yuj. Max wal-lej bay eb chi ecꞌcꞌal cuywok entak, tol chi yican el eb yin nak, palta maj jeꞌ yuj eb, ẍi bay.
Axa yalon Juan bay Jesús axca tiꞌ:
Lananxa toj Jesús yul be, ay jun winak yanejxacꞌal max jay bay, max bekon ay jajnaj ba satak Cham, max yaloni:
—Ok techajok, ẍi eb.
—¿Tzet che yunej? ¿Tzet xan che xuyil no burro tiꞌ? ẍi yutelay eb.
Axa yalon bay eb tuꞌ:
—Yechel sat cham yajaw bay Roma yetokcꞌal is bi cham, ẍi eb bay.
Caytuꞌ max yut yalon David tuꞌ, tol a Cristo, is Yajawil yayji. Yuj tuꞌ, txequel tol man asannejok tol yinatil David yayji Cham, ẍi Jesús bay eb.
Yujtol axca jun miman yailal ok jay yet jun tiempoal tuꞌ, cꞌamto bay maxax uj junelok, yecheltaxcꞌal max watxꞌnej Dios yulyibankꞌinal tiꞌ. Asan chꞌan junel tuꞌ, cꞌamxa bakꞌin ok uj junelxa axca tuꞌ.
Atacꞌalaꞌ tzet max jeꞌ yuj ix yakꞌon ayin, a max yakꞌ ix. Ayokto chi yaon oc ix jun sukꞌukꞌi jab tiꞌ yin in mimanil tiꞌ, yet watxꞌ watxꞌxa wayji cax chin toj muklayok.
—Wal yel chi wal ayach, a yet jun akꞌbal tiꞌ, oxelxa quin eon el en yin aloni, tol mayin ojtakok, cax ok okꞌ no caẍlan yet cayelal, ẍi bay.
Palta ay jun nak achꞌej tzakancꞌal yintak Cham. Tꞌeban octok yul jun sábana chulan oc yin, max oc mitxꞌnaj eb yin nak.
—Wal yel, ach tiꞌ etbi a ba yetok eb. Aj Galilea ach cꞌapaxok, ẍi eb bay.
—Tzalojan ach Reyal eb israel, ẍixacꞌal eb bay.
max jay jun mimek winak xol eb yet yajawilal chi yik José aj Arimatea. Echbanebil yoc Dios Yajawil yuj. Cꞌam jabok chi xiwi, max octok satak Pilato, bet kꞌanon mimanil Jesús bay.
A yet ayoc cham Herodes yin reyal bay yul yet Judea, ay jun sacerdote chi yik Zacarías, yetbi ba yetok jun makan eb sacerdote chi yik Abías. Elizabet bi yistzil cham tuꞌ. Yinatil Aarón cꞌapax xal.
—María, manchak ach xiwi, yujtol xiwil watxꞌcꞌulal Dios max txꞌox ayach.
A yet max ajapnok tiempoal yalji yuneꞌ Elizabet, winak unin jun max alji.
Max beticꞌ yetok María. Watxꞌxa yayji trato eb, yobixxa ix.
Max lajwi tuꞌ, max kꞌanon cham watxꞌcꞌulal Dios yiban eb. Max yalon bay María, txutx Jesús axca tiꞌ:
Ta chi na ba e cꞌul yin e yobtakil, yowalil watxꞌ che yut e beybal, yet watxꞌ chi txecloj elok tol yel mayal e na e ba. Manchak e yal axca tiꞌ: Cꞌam tzet chi co naꞌ, yinatil on Abraham, man quex chiok. Yujtol chi wal ayex, ta chi yal cꞌul Dios, chi jeꞌ yuten oc juntzan chꞌen tiꞌ animail, cax chi oc yinatilok Abraham e qꞌuexelok.
Jacob, Isaac, Abraham, Taré, Nacor,
Yetok cꞌapaxok, yuj ul waloncan elok tol mayal jay tiempoal jun colbanilej chi yakꞌ Cham Dios Jajawil, ẍi txꞌan Un Tzꞌibbilcan tuꞌ, max awtelay aj yuj Jesús.
Palta max tenchanelay eb yuj Cham. Maj chaꞌ kꞌanjab eb, yujtol yojtak eb tol a ton Cristo.
A yet max yilon Jesús tol max yaoc eb nak cꞌul yin, axa yalon Cham bay nak sicbinak el is mimanil tuꞌ:
Yetok cꞌapaxok, a mac mayal uqꞌuen vino ayxa cꞌubay ecꞌok, tok chito yochej jun ato watxꞌji tuꞌ. Chi yalon eb axca tiꞌ: A vino ayxa watxꞌji tiꞌ, yelxacꞌal watxꞌ, ẍi eb, ẍi Jesús.
Wujcꞌal ayin Chekbilintek yuj Dios xol eb jet animail tiꞌ, xan ok chichon oc cꞌul eb anima e yin, ok ex yuktej el eb xol, cax ok ex buchlay yuj eb. Wujcꞌal, xan caw yobcꞌal tzet ok yal eb e yin, palta a yet caytuꞌ ok ex yut eb axca tuꞌ, caw watxꞌ e yet.
A bay tuꞌ ay jun cham capitán aj Roma. Ay jun is moso cham caw xajan yuj sicꞌlibil, palta yaꞌay, cax toxa chi cami.
A yet mayal paxcantok eb chekbej tuꞌ, max yalontek Jesús yuj Juan tuꞌ bay eb anima axca tiꞌ: Naektek, tzet max bet e yil bay tzꞌinan txꞌotxꞌ. ¿A mi junok te aj chi ecꞌ meeok yuj cakꞌekꞌ max bet e yilaꞌ?
—Ti chi lajwican a yobtakil eban, ẍi bay ix.
—Tonek bay junxa kꞌaxepal aꞌ mar, ẍi bay eb.
Yujtol a jun cꞌotan is cutzꞌin, tol chi cami, cax janicꞌxanej iquis. Ay mi 12 abil is kꞌinal ix is cutzꞌin tuꞌ. A yet max toj Jesús yetok cham bay na tuꞌ, xiwil anima max toj yetok. Chi witzꞌxacꞌal ba eb toj bululok yetok.
Max lajwi tu xin, axa toj eb tuꞌ; max ecꞌ eb bay junjun aldea. Max yalcan el eb kꞌanejal yet colbanilej. Max watxꞌji cꞌapax can eb yaꞌay bay junjun lugar yuj eb.
Ta ay mac chi qꞌuixwi aj wuj, cꞌal yuj in kꞌanej, ok in qꞌuixwok cꞌapax aj yuj eb, ayin Chekbilintek yuj Dios xol eb jet animail tiꞌ, yet ok in jay ul wakꞌon Reyal. A yet tuꞌ ok in jay yetok maykꞌakꞌal in Mam, cꞌal yetok maykꞌakꞌal eb is yángel tol sicꞌbil el yuj.
—Mamin Meẍtol, ay jun winak max jilaꞌ, tol lanan yion el espíritu yob yin anima yin ach yakꞌon binajok. Palta max co tencan oc wanajok, yujtol man junnejok chi ecꞌ jetok, ẍi bay.
A yet chex apni bay junjun conob bay chex chalayi, tzancꞌal tzet chi etxbelay eltek ayex, loek.
Lajwi tu xin, ay jun cham yinatil Leví max ecꞌ cꞌapax yul jun be tuꞌ. Max oc cꞌapax can tꞌanan junxa tuꞌ yin nak, cax tocꞌal max qꞌuexbenej ba, max toji.
A yet junel, ay jun nak anima ayoc espíritu yob yin. Cꞌam jabok chi jeꞌ kꞌanjab nak yuj. A Jesús max yiil jun espíritu yob tuꞌ yin nak. A yet max el yin nak, max jeꞌ kꞌanjab aj nak, xan xiwil max cꞌayaj cꞌul eb anima yuj.
Caw cꞌam e nabal, ¿tom man e yojtakok tol a jun mactxel watxꞌnenej juntzan tzet yetal chi jil tiꞌ, aꞌ cꞌapax max watxꞌnen juntzan tzet yetal cꞌam chi jilaꞌ?
—Meẍtol, al bay jun wuẍtak, tol chi yakꞌ jabok wet yin jantak tzet max can yuj co mam on, ẍi bay Jesús.
Yuj tuꞌ max kꞌanlej Pedro bay Cham axca tiꞌ:
Ay jun ix ix ayicꞌ bay tuꞌ, 18 abilxa yacꞌal ay yuj jun espíritu yob. Max coxloj ix yuj, max aycan nojan ix. Cꞌamxa chi jichloj aj lecan ix.
A wal ayex tiꞌ ex aj Jerusalén, che makꞌ wal cam eb chekbej Dios. Axa juntzanxa eb chekbiltek yuj Dios e xol, che kꞌokchꞌennej eb. Xiwilxa el max wochej max quex wawtejtek ayin, axca junok no caẍlan chi kꞌuttejtek yuneꞌ, cax chi mojoni, palta maj yal e cꞌul.
Chi wal ayach, cꞌam junok eb babel awtebil wuj tuꞌ ok jeꞌ low bay jun miman loj chi wakꞌ tiꞌ, ẍi cham patrón tuꞌ. Caytuꞌ yalon jun abix tiꞌ, ẍi Jesús.
Yel mi watxꞌ ok in pax bay in mam tuꞌ, cax ok walon bay axca tiꞌ: Mam, caw wal max oc in mul bay Dios, cax max oc cꞌapax in mul ayach.
Axa yalon Cham bay eb axca tiꞌ: Ayex tiꞌ, asan satak eb anima watxꞌ che yut e ba, palta yojtak Dios tzetbil yili e yanimail. A juntzan tzet miman yelapnok yul sat anima, cꞌam chi chaꞌ cꞌul Dios.
A yet lanancꞌal toj Jesús yul beal Jerusalén, max eqꞌuel Cham bay is mojon Samaria yetok Galilea.
A eb cꞌam chi yochej chi cami, chi bekil eb jun kꞌinalej tol aycꞌal yin tojbalkꞌinal. A pax eb chi bekcꞌulok cam wuj xin, a ton eb tuꞌ ok ion kꞌinalej tol aycꞌal yin tojbalkꞌinal.
A yet max yaben nak juntzan tuꞌ, caw wal max cusaj cꞌul nak, yujtol caw wal beyom sicꞌlibil.
Axa Zaqueo tuꞌ, caw wal chi yochejcꞌal chi yil yin Jesús, tzetbil wal yili, palta cꞌamcꞌal chi jeꞌ yiloni, yujtol xiwil anima oyan oc yin Cham yet chi beyi, yetok cꞌapaxok, yuj yaliẍ tel Zaqueo tuꞌ.
A yet cꞌamto chi toj eb, cax max yalon bay eb axca tiꞌ:
Axa cꞌoli yalubtanen eb is xol tuꞌ yuj tzet max yal tuꞌ. Max yalon eb axca tiꞌ: ¿Tzet chi jut jalon bay? Ta chi jalaꞌ tol a Dios akꞌnej yikbej Juan tuꞌ, ok mi yal ayon axca tiꞌ: ¿Tzet yuj xan cꞌam che ya pax oc yin e cꞌul xin? ẍi mi.
Max lajwi tuꞌ, ay juntzan eb saduceo max jayoc bay Jesús, eb chi aloni tol cꞌam chi ictzoj aj eb camnak. Axa yalon eb bay Cham axca tiꞌ:
Ay juntzan eb lanan yalontek yuj templo Dios tuꞌ, tol manxa watxꞌilok yili, caw wal watxꞌ cawxi yuj chꞌen chꞌen ayoc yin, yetok yuj tzet sabil yuj anima ayoc yin, xan max yaltek Jesús bay eb axca tiꞌ:
Che yilcꞌal e ba. Manchak e chaꞌ pitbok e ba yuj pekꞌal, yuj uqꞌuem anil, ma yuj junokxa tzet yetal chex oc il yuj bay yulyibankꞌinal tiꞌ. Ta cꞌamak, axa ok jay jun cꞌual tuꞌ, cax man watxꞌok e yayji.
Axa tinani xin, a mac ok in aon oc yul kꞌabej tuꞌ, ayoc yin meẍa tiꞌ jetok.
Caw wal max oc pitzꞌan cuscꞌulal yin is cꞌul. Yuj tuꞌ xan max yiajtek cꞌulok txajli sicꞌlibil. Caw wal chi el yal, caw wal chi ay tꞌujlabok axca mimek tzꞌuj, caytuꞌ yel chiqꞌuil yalok, chi aycꞌay sat txꞌotxꞌ.
Axa yel besnaj xol eb tuꞌ, cax yeltok yokꞌ sicꞌlibil yina.
Ato yet jun cꞌual tuꞌ max yamigonej aj ba Pilato yetok Herodes, yujtol a yet yalantok, yajcꞌul ba eb.
—Max ab tzꞌak col juntzan anima, axa tinaniꞌ, tatol yel a Cristo tiꞌ, cax aꞌ sicꞌbil el yuj Dios, colokab ba jilaꞌ, ẍi eb.
Max apni oc eb, max yilon eb, elnakxa chꞌen is makil jun chꞌen bay max mukayi.
A Cham Cristo, yowalil tol tꞌinan yaben yail juntzan tuꞌ yet manto oc Yajawilal, ẍi bay eb.
Yetok cꞌapaxok, yowalil tol yetok wikbej ok al-lay el kꞌanej Dios xol anima bay junjun nación. Ok al-lay el xol eb tol yowalil chi na ba eb yin is yobtakil, yet watxꞌ chi jolay cꞌay yobtakil eb tuꞌ yiban. A bay Jerusalén tiꞌ ok babjok yal-lay el wabixal; catatuꞌ ok pukaxtok bay junjun conob.
—¿Mac ach wal txel xin? ¿Ma ach Elías ach? ẍi eb bay.
Axa toj eb yetok tuꞌ, max bet yilon eb bay cajan, cax max can eb yetok yet jun yaycꞌualil tuꞌ, yujtol a las cuatroxa mi yet max apni eb yetok.
—Che yikejcꞌal masanil tzet ok yal Jesús ayex, ẍi bay eb.
Ay jun kꞌekbintakil max ulicꞌ bay Jesús, max yalon axca tiꞌ:
Axa yalon bay eb tuꞌ:
Axa yalon ix bay tuꞌ:
Ay eb ecꞌnakxa mulnaj xol eb, axca mac chi tzicwi ay trigo. Ay cꞌapax eb chi mulnaj xol eb axca tol joom trigo eb, yet watxꞌ chi chaꞌ eb anima tiꞌ jun kꞌinalej tol aycꞌal yin tojbalkꞌinal. A eb chi mulnaj tuꞌ, ok chaꞌ eb paktzil jun is mulnajil tuꞌ, yet watxꞌ jun lajancꞌal ok yun tzaloj eb masanil.
—¿Chi mi ochej chi jaycan a cꞌul? ẍi bay nak.
Ayin tiꞌ, cꞌam junok tzet yetal chi jeꞌ wunen yul wet. Axca chi yut yalon in Mam ayin, caytuꞌ chi yun in beycꞌulnewi. Baycꞌal ijan chi yun in beycꞌulnewi, yujtol manak tzet chi cha in cꞌul chin sayaꞌ, palta a tzet chi cha cꞌul Cham cheknejintek, a ton in Mam.
—Alek bay eb anima tuꞌ, tol chi ay chotan eb masanil, ẍi bay eb.
Yuj tuꞌ xan max yal Jesús bay eb:
Tzancꞌal mac ok chion in chibejal tiꞌ, cax ok yuqꞌuen cꞌapax in chiqꞌuil tiꞌ, chi ayjicꞌal ecꞌ win, cax chin ayji cꞌapax ecꞌ yin.
—Manto cꞌualok in txꞌoxon el in ba. Axa ayex xin, tzancꞌal mi tzet cꞌual chi jeꞌ e naoni.
A pax in xin, wojtak Cham, yujtol a tuꞌ max in tita. A Cham cheknejintek, ẍi Jesús bay eb.
Ay jun yet fariseoal eb tuꞌ chi yik Nicodemo, jun betnak ecꞌ kꞌanjab yetok Jesús yet yalantok. A jun tuꞌ max alon bay eb axca tiꞌ:
A co ley ayicꞌ yul co kꞌab chi aloni, tatol ay cawanok testigo lajancꞌal yaloni, yowalil chi co cha jab tzet chi yal eb.
Ayin tiꞌ wojtak toni, tol yinatil ex Abraham; palta ilab che yochej chin e yakꞌ pax camok, yujtol a tzet chi wal ayex, cꞌam yelapnok yul e sat.
—A jun winak tiꞌ, man yujok mul is mam ma is txutx, xan caytuꞌ yayji, tamwal yuj cꞌapax is mul nak, palta tol chi yochej Dios chi txꞌox is maykꞌakꞌal yin nak, xan caytuꞌ yayji.
—Ayin tiꞌ, chekbej Dios yayji in naoni, ẍi nak.
A yet max yaben jaywan eb fariseo ayicꞌ bay tuꞌ juntzan kꞌanej tuꞌ, max yalon eb bay axca tiꞌ:
—Mayal wal ayex, palta cꞌam che yaoc yin e cꞌul. A juntzan milagro chin txꞌoxoꞌ, asan yuj yikbej in Mam xan chi jeꞌ wuj in txꞌoxoni, cax a ton juntzan tuꞌ chi txꞌoxkꞌabnen elok mac in txel.
—Tonek bay yul yet Judea junelxa, ẍi bay eb.
tutun cꞌamto chi oc Cham xol conob tuꞌ. A bay max bet chalay yuj Marta, a tuꞌ ayto ecꞌok.
Palta ay jun chi yik Caifás xol eb. A jun tuꞌ ayoc sat sacerdoteal yet jun abil tuꞌ. Aꞌ max alon bay eb axca tiꞌ:
Max yalon eb fariseo axca tiꞌ:
Cay ton tuꞌ max yun yeloc tzet albilcan yuj Isaías, is chekbej Dios, yet max yaloncan axca tiꞌ:
E Meẍtol in toni, e Yajawil in toni, palta ilab max in txꞌajil e yakan tiꞌ. Yuj tuꞌ, moj wal caytuꞌ che yut e ba cꞌapaxok.
—A bay ok in apnok, majto jeꞌ e toj wetok tinaniꞌ. Cꞌojancꞌulalto ok jeꞌ e toj wetok bay tuꞌ, ẍi Jesús bay.
Axa yalon Cham axca tiꞌ:
Caw wal che natek jun kꞌanej max wal ayex tiꞌ: Cꞌam junok mosejal ecꞌban yintak is patrón, quin chi ayex. Axca max yun yoc eb ajcꞌulal win, caytuꞌ ok yun cꞌapax yoc eb ajcꞌulal e yin. Ta max yikej eb tzet max wal ayin tiꞌ, ok yikej cꞌapax eb tzet ok e yalaꞌ.
Wal yel chi wal ayex, ok ex cusok, ok ex okꞌok, axa eb yet yulyibankꞌinal ti xin, ok tzaloj eb. Ok ex ton cusok, palta a jun e cuscꞌulal tuꞌ, tzalojcꞌulalxa ok yutaj ba.
Man lananok walon ayach, tol cheil eb yulyibankꞌinal tiꞌ yin aymanil, palta tol chin kꞌan ayach, tol cha taynej eb, yet watxꞌ cꞌam eb chi etax el yuj nak yelxacꞌal yob.
Lajwi tu xin, cax max yiontok eb bay yatut Anás, cham niꞌ Caifás. A Caifás tuꞌ, sat sacerdote yayji yet jun abil tuꞌ.
—A ayon israel on tiꞌ, cꞌam jikbej jakꞌon cam junok mactxel, ẍi eb bay.
—Ayon tiꞌ ay co ley, cax atacꞌalaꞌ yalon co ley tuꞌ, tol moj chi cami, yujtol max yaloc ba Cꞌajolok Dios, ẍi eb bay.
Axca ton tiꞌ max yun yunen el tzet tzꞌibbilcan yul txꞌan Un, bay chi yal axca tiꞌ: A in pichil max pojcan ecꞌ eb yin, a yin in jokan pichil max yakꞌ eb suerte, ẍican yul txꞌan Un tuꞌ. Yuj tuꞌ xan caytuꞌ max yut eb soldado tuꞌ.
Yanej eb toj cawanil; palta max cancan Pedro tuꞌ yuj junxa tuꞌ, xan a jun tuꞌ max babji yapni yin aymanil.
—Chaekcan Cham Espíritu Santo.
Max yabcꞌal Simón Pedro axca tuꞌ, axa yaon oc is pichil tuꞌ, yujtol asan yul is pichil ayocok. Axa kꞌokon el ba yul barco tuꞌ, cax max el ti aꞌ.
Max yalon bay axca tiꞌ:
Chi yalon cꞌapax axca tiꞌ:
A cꞌu ok kꞌekbok, axa xajaw axcaxacꞌal chicꞌ ok yuncan elok, ẍi Cham Jajawil. A juntzan tiꞌ ok yun yet cꞌamto chi jay jun cꞌual yet yowal cꞌul Cham. A jun cꞌual tuꞌ, caw wal miman yelapnok, cax ok cꞌayaj cꞌul anima yuj.
Aylaj eb chi txonil is txꞌotxꞌ, cꞌal juntzanokxa tzet ay eb, cax chi pojon ecꞌ eb is tojol tuꞌ xolak eb, atacꞌalaꞌ is cawxinakil junjun eb.
A yet max txꞌoxon aj Dios is Cꞌajol, a ayon max babji chekontek, yuj yakꞌon is watxꞌcꞌulal ayon yuj on yioncan el yin co yobtakil junjun on, ẍi Pedro bay eb yet conob tuꞌ.
¿Tzet wal yuj xan chi weklab eb conoblak? ¿Tzet wal yuj xan chi lajtinej eb tzet yetal tol cꞌam yechel ok yunej?
Xiwil eb winak, cꞌal eb ix chi yaoc cꞌul yin Cham Jajawil.
Max cha cꞌul eb yajaw tuꞌ tzet max yal cham Gamaliel tuꞌ, axa yawtelay octok eb chekbej Jesús tuꞌ yuj eb, cax max yikon eb tzꞌum. Max al-lay cꞌapax bay eb, tol manchakxa yalil eb yabixal Jesús. Lajwi tu xin, max beklay el eb.
A eb jichmam tuꞌ, ay jun yuẍtak eb chi yik José. A yet junel, max meltzoj oc eb ajcꞌulal yin. Yuj tuꞌ xan txonnaktok eb bay conob Egipto. Palta aycꞌal oc Dios yetok.
Palta a eb jichmam tuꞌ, maj yal cꞌul eb max yikej tzet max yal Moisés tuꞌ. Yuj tuꞌ xan max yintaknej el eb, cax max yochen eb max meltzoj yintak junelxa bay Egipto.
A Felipe, a bay conob Samaria max apni, max cꞌoli yalon el yabixal Cristo nan xol eb anima bay tuꞌ.
—¿Chi mi nachaj el oj tzet chi yal txꞌan Un tuꞌ? ẍi bay.
Ok wakꞌ yojtaknej elok tol wujcꞌal, xan yowalil ok yil xiwil yailal, ẍi Cham Jajawil tuꞌ.
—Tabita, ajan wanok, ẍi bay xal.
Axa yilay oc eb yul na yuj Pedro tuꞌ. A tuꞌ max way eb, axa yet junxa cꞌual, max toj yetok eb, max toj cꞌapax jaywan creyente aj Jope yetok eb.
Yuj tuꞌ xan max yal Pedro tol chi akꞌlay bautizar eb yin bi Jesucristo. Lajwi yakꞌlay bautizar eb tuꞌ, cax max yalon eb bay, tol chi can jayebok cꞌu yetok eb.
Ay jun yetbeyom eb chi yik Agabo, max aj wan nan xol eb creyente tuꞌ, max akꞌlay yal yuj Yespíritu Dios axca tiꞌ:
Yet max lajwi yaben eb kꞌanjab cham, max yalon eb axca tiꞌ: A jun mac chi kꞌanjab eltek tuꞌ, man animaok, palta a junok eb dios chi kꞌanjabi, ẍi eb.
A jun yinatil David tuꞌ chi yik Jesús, aꞌ chekbiltek co Colomalok ayon israel on tiꞌ yuj Dios, axcataꞌ max yut yakꞌoncan is tiꞌ.
Axa tziconcan el Pablo cꞌal Bernabé tuꞌ pokokal yakan, yuj txꞌoxkꞌabnen el eb, tol cꞌamxa yalon eb yet yin eb anima tuꞌ. Lajwi tu xin, max toj eb bay conob Iconio.
Max yalcan el eb kꞌanej Dios bay conob Perge. Lajwi tuꞌ max toj eb, max apni eb bay conob Atalia.
Yuj tuꞌ xan max wajan alnej eb chekbej Jesús, yetok eb anciano, cꞌal eb creyente masanil, tol chi siqꞌuil eb jaywan eb creyente chi toj yucꞌlebok Pablo yetok Bernabé bay conob Antioquía. Lajwi tuꞌ, max sicꞌon el eb Judas, nak chi yik cꞌapax Barsabás, yetok Silas. A cawan eb tuꞌ, miman yelapnok eb nan xol eb creyente.
Lajwicꞌal yilon Pablo jun tuꞌ, cax max watxꞌnen ba eb wetok, yet chon toj bay Macedonia tuꞌ, yujtol max jojtaknej elok, tol a Dios akꞌnej jopiso jalon el kꞌanejal yet colbanilej bay eb anima tuꞌ.
—Aoc a cꞌul yin Cham Jajawil Jesucristo, cax ok ach colchajok, cꞌal yetok jantak mac ayicꞌ etok bay a na, ẍi eb bay nak.
—Che yal bay Silas yetok bay Timoteo, tol chi tit eb yin ayman, ẍi yutelay eb.
Palta tutun lajancꞌal mulnajil eb xin, yet watxꞌnem mantiadoal ba eb, xan max ayji ecꞌ Pablo yetok eb bay tuꞌ, cax chi mulnaj yetok eb.
A yet ayicꞌ Apolos bay Corinto, max cꞌoli yecꞌ Pablo bay juntzan conoblak ay bay tzalquiẍtak, max apni oc bay conob Efeso. A tuꞌ max yil-lej el ba yetok juntzan eb creyente bay tuꞌ.
—Ex wet chacꞌom chꞌenal, ti wal e yojtak, tol xiwil co tumin chi jiꞌ yin jun jopiso tiꞌ.
Ayon tiꞌ, max on oc yul barco, max on toj bay conob Asón. A tuꞌ max jechbanej yapni Pablo, axca max jut jalon yetok, yujtol yakan max yaocok max toji.
—Matawal cꞌam chach toj bay Jerusalén tuꞌ, ẍi eb bay.
Caw wal max tit yowal masanil conob, cax max wajban oc ba eb, max bet tzicon eltek eb Pablo yul templo Dios tuꞌ, cax kꞌoklay eltek yina yuj eb. Ayman max makchej eb puerta bay.
Axa yalon ayin axca tiꞌ: A Cham co Diosal, acꞌal ton oc Cham tuꞌ Diosal eb jichmam, a Cham sicꞌnej ach elok, yet watxꞌ chojtaknej elok tzet chi yochej Cham en. Yuj cꞌapax tol chi yochej Cham tol chel yin Jesús, Cham tojol, cꞌal yuj chaben yul is nukꞌ tzet tꞌinan yalon ayach.
Axa yalon Pablo tuꞌ axca tiꞌ:
Cax che yaon aj tzꞌum no chej bay ok aj Pablo, yujtol yowalil ok e yitok satak cham Félix, yujtol a yajaw yayji. Jelancꞌal che yut e ba, ayta tzet ok on Pablo tuꞌ yulak be, ẍi cham coronel tuꞌ bay eb.
Yuj tu xan caw wal chin beycꞌulnej tzet chi yal yikbomal in nabal, yet watxꞌ manchak oc in yobtakil yul sat Dios, cꞌal bay eb wet animail.
—Ti wal ach cha kꞌantok a ba satak cham yajaw bay Roma. Yuj tu xin, ok ach watok, ẍi bay.
A in naon yet yalantok, tol xiwil tzet tꞌinan wunen yuj wajcꞌulal yin eb yet-xa Jesús aj Nazaret. A in naoni, tol watxꞌ chi wut in ba.
Max wajan alnej eb yajaw tol chi alaytok Pablo bay Italia, bay conob Roma, xan max alay oc Pablo tuꞌ yetok jaywanxa yet aj presoal yul kꞌab jun cham capitán chi yik Julio. A cham Julio tuꞌ, yetbeyom ba yetok jun bulan eb soldado chi yik yet Augusto.
Chi xiw eb talaj cꞌuxan chi makꞌay ba teꞌ yibanlak chꞌen chꞌen yul aꞌ. Yuj tuꞌ xan max bekaytok tꞌununok eb caneb mitxꞌbanil oc wanaj te barco tuꞌ chopiltok teꞌ. Lajwi tuꞌ max yechbanen eb sakbi. Yochejxacꞌal eb tol ayman max sakbi elok.
Max on apni bay conob Siracusa. Oxeb cꞌu max on ecꞌ bay tuꞌ.
Ayin tiꞌ, chi wakꞌ serbil Dios yin masanil in cꞌul yin walon el yabixal is Cꞌajol. In testigo yayji Dios, tol a yet chin txajli junjuntak el, chin txajli cꞌapax e yuj.
Ok yakꞌ Dios kꞌinalej tol aycꞌal yin tojbalkꞌinal ayon, tatol tecꞌan chi jut co ba junen watxꞌilal, yujtol chi jochej ay jalon jet yin is watxꞌilal Dios. Chi jochej tol ay jelapnok yul sat Cham. Chi jochej tol chi co cha co kꞌinal tol aycꞌal yin tojbalkꞌinal.
Ay eb chi naon axca tiꞌ: A yet chi wakꞌon lekꞌtial, lanan in txꞌoxon elok, tol asan Dios yel chi yalaꞌ. Tatol chi ilay can Dios yuj lekꞌtial chi wakꞌ tu xin, ¿tzet xan a yet chin beycꞌulnelayi, chin al-lay yobtakwomal? ẍi eb.
A tinaniꞌ, kꞌinalok ta chon mulnaj bay junok anima, cax chi co chaon co tojol, a co tojol tuꞌ, man sabalok, palta tol jecxa nak aj mulnajil tuꞌ.
Palta txꞌoxnak Dios camcꞌulal ayon, yujtol a Cristo max yakꞌ cam ba juj yet caw wal yobtakwom onto.
Palta chi wal yuj diosalil bay Dios e yuj. Yujtol caxcꞌal max e yakꞌ serbil yobtakil yet yalan, palta axa tinaniꞌ, lanan e yiken yin masanil e cꞌul juntzan cuybanilej bay max ex alaycan ocok.
Caw okꞌbal cꞌul chi wun yuj. A jun in mimanil tiꞌ chin iontok bay camich yin junelnej. Palta, ¿mac chi jeꞌ yuj on colon el yul kꞌab co mimanil tiꞌ?
A mac on sicꞌbil on el yuj, awtebil on cꞌapax yuj. Aꞌ cꞌapax chi alon juj ayon awtebil on yuj tiꞌ, tol watxꞌ on yul sat, cax chi yakꞌoni tol ay jalon jet yin is watxꞌil.
Xan caytuꞌ Dios yetok eb anima. Ay eb moj chaon yowal cꞌul Dios, moj eb tojcan bay yailal yin junelnej. Caxcꞌal chi yochej Dios chi txꞌoxkꞌabnej el yowal cꞌul yin eb, yuj txꞌoxon el eb is maykꞌakꞌal Cham, palta caw miman chi yut cꞌul, chi yakꞌcꞌal techaj yobtakil eb.
Palta man masanilok eb chi iken jun kꞌanejal yet colbanilej tiꞌ. Axcataꞌ yaloncan Isaías: Mamin, ¿mactxel max yaoc cꞌul yin kꞌanej max al-lay can elok? ẍi.
Ilab maj yakꞌ Dios mimancꞌulal yin eb yetcꞌaltaꞌa. Akxam ex wali, man ok yakꞌ mimancꞌulal e yin cꞌapaxok, ta che yiel e cꞌul yin.
A mac yob chi yut cꞌul ayon, aokab watxꞌcꞌulal Dios chi co kꞌantek yiban, cax manokabnak yowal cꞌul Dios chi co kꞌantek yiban, palta aokab is watxꞌcꞌulal.
Yujtol max cam Cristo, cax max ictzoj pax ajok, yet watxꞌ chi oc Cham Yajawilok eb camnak, cꞌal Jajawilok mac on iquis on cꞌapax tiꞌ.
Tzꞌibbil cꞌapaxcan yuj Isaías yul txꞌan Un tuꞌ axca tiꞌ:
Chi watok cawil cꞌul juẍtak Amplias. Ay cꞌapax in camcꞌulal yin, yujtol ayoc Cham Jajawil yin is cꞌul.
Txꞌok txꞌokxacꞌal e kꞌanjab junjun ex chi wabtok. Ilab tol ay ex lananxa e yalon aj axca tiꞌ: Ayin tiꞌ yet in Pablo, quex chi. Ay ex xin: Ayin tiꞌ yet in Apolos, quex chi. Ay ex pax xin: Ayin tiꞌ yet in Pedro, quex chi. Ay ex xin: Ayin tiꞌ yet in Cristo, quex chi.
Ay wal jun tzet watxꞌnebil yuj Dios, yuj yakꞌon bay eb ay is camcꞌulal yin.
Yuj tuꞌ maj jeꞌ e yaon oc e nabal yin junok anima, cax che yion can e ba yuj. Yujtol mayal yakꞌ Dios masanil tzet yetal e sataknej jetok.
Yuj tu xin, bekekcan juntzan e beybal yet yalantok tuꞌ. Yujtol a juntzan tuꞌ, lajan axca yich pan. Xan ta che bekcan axca walon tuꞌ, ok ex occan axca wal ixim pan chi lolay yet kꞌin Pascua, tol cꞌam jabok paltail. Yujtol wal yel cayex ton tuꞌ yul sat Cristo, yujtol a Cham max cam co qꞌuexelok. Axcataꞌ no calnel chi akꞌlay cam yin xajanbalil yet is Pascua eb wet israelal, axca tuꞌ max yun cam Cristo juj.
Yuj tuꞌ, cꞌam chi jeꞌ e tenon tzet chi yochej e yetbi e yin. Asan ta lajtiꞌ chex el bian, cax chi oc wanaj e yuj jayebok cꞌual yuj e txajli bay Dios yin masanil e cꞌul. Chicꞌal lajwi jayeb cꞌu tuꞌ, junanejek pax e ba junelxa, yet watxꞌ manchak ex etnelay el yuj Satanás, tol cꞌam chi jeꞌ e mitxꞌon oc waan e mimanil.
A juntzan chi waltok ayex tiꞌ, man yujok ex in tenon oc waanok, xan chi waltok; cꞌamak. Palta yuj e watxꞌilok xan chi waltok, yujtol chi wochej che beybalnej axca wal chi yochej cꞌul Cham Jajawil, cax che yakꞌon serbil Cham yin masanil e cꞌul.
Ay cꞌapax juntzanxa eb ay yalon yet chaon yet ayex, palta yelxacꞌal ay jalon jet ayon tiꞌ.
Yuj tu xin ex in camcꞌulnebil, caw che yiel e ba bay junok tzet chi al-lay oc diosal.
Yuj tuꞌ xan moj yaon aj eb ix kꞌoxil is jolom, yuj txꞌoxkꞌabnen el eb ix, tol ayoc eb ix yalan yikbej yichamil. Moj axca tuꞌ chi yut ba eb ix, yuj tꞌanan cꞌapax oc eb ángel jin.
Yetok cꞌapaxok, txꞌok txꞌokcꞌal co mulnajil junjun on. Palta acꞌal oc Dios chi oc jetok junjun on yin tzet chi jun tuꞌ.
Ta caw yel ay co camcꞌulal, cꞌam chi jiel qꞌuixwil junok mactxel. Chi jochej tol man asannejok on ay jalon jet. Manokab cꞌunok tit jowal. Cꞌam chi co naꞌ jion ecꞌ co pak bay junok mactxel.
Yuj tuꞌ xan a juntzan txꞌok tiejal chi al-lay tuꞌ, txꞌoxbanilcꞌal yayji bay eb man creyenteok, cax man txꞌoxbanilok yayji bay eb creyentexa. A pax yal-lay el kꞌanej Dios tu xin, txꞌoxbanil ton yayji bay eb creyente jun tuꞌ, cax man txꞌoxbanilok bay eb man creyenteok.
Yuj tuꞌ, caxcꞌal ayin max walaꞌ, ma tol a juntzanxa eb chekbej Jesús max aloni, acꞌal oc jun kꞌanejal yet colbanilej tuꞌ chi jalaꞌ. A ton jun tiꞌ che yaoc yin e cꞌul.
A juntzan tzet ay satcan tuꞌ, txꞌok txꞌok yel tzekekial junjun. Txꞌok yel tzekekial cꞌu, txꞌok yel tzekekial xajaw. Txꞌok cꞌapax yel tzekekial junjun waycan.
Makwajanekcꞌal. Tecꞌanokabcꞌal che yut e yaon oc e cꞌul yin Cham Jajawil. Manchak ex xiw jabok. Caw che tecꞌbaj e ba junjun ex.
A Cristo Jesús Cꞌajol Dios, aꞌ ecꞌ jalnak on yabixal e nan e xol. Ecꞌ yalnak cꞌapax Silvano yetok Timoteo. A Cristo, cꞌam junelok max yal axca tiꞌ: Jaꞌ ẍi junok bek, axa junokxa bek xin, chi qꞌuexon is tiꞌ cax chi yaloni: Cꞌamakxa, ẍi paxok. Yujtol asan tzet yetal yel max el yaloni.
Ta miman yelapnok jun ley tuꞌ yet max jayi, yelxacꞌal miman yelapnok jun abix max yi jay Cham Yespíritu Dios ayon.
Yel toni, a yet ayon ecꞌ yin co mimanil tiꞌ, chon alxi yetok, yujtol chi jochej chon ecꞌtok bay junxa co mimanil, a ton jun ok co kꞌan bay satcan, jun axca na tuꞌ.
Ay bay chi yal eb anima tol may on yojtakok eb, palta caw ojtakbil on yuj eb sicꞌlibil. Ay bay chi yakꞌlej eb on yaon oc eb yul kꞌab camich, palta acꞌalaꞌ iquis oncꞌal. Caw wal chi alay oc yailal jiban on, palta cꞌam chon cami.
Caxcꞌal caw max akꞌlay porobal eb yuj juntzan yailal max jayoc yiban eb, palta caw chi tzaloj eb. Caxcꞌal caw mebaꞌ eb sicꞌlibil, palta bekan yel yuj eb, axca tol beyom eb chi jilaꞌ.
A Dios chi jeꞌ yuj yakꞌon masanil tzet yetal ayex yuj is watxꞌcꞌulal. Chi yakꞌ masanil tzet caw chi oc yopiso e yuj yin masanil tiempo. Toltax chi yakꞌxacꞌal sobra ayex. Yuj tuꞌ, xiwil bay chi jeꞌ e colwaj ocok.
Yujtol ay eb chi ecꞌ alon juntzanokxa txꞌok cuybanilej ayex. Axca tol txꞌok junokxa Jesús chi ecꞌ yal eb, cax manak jun chi ecꞌ jalilok, palta lanan e chaon e yab bay eb. Lanan e chaon junokxa espíritu bay eb, palta man axcaok Cham chabilxa e yuj. Lanan e yaon oc e cꞌul yin jun yabixal colbanilej, palta manak jun e yabnakcan ayon.
Palta a yul jun xuc max in aytok, cax weltok yul wentenail murallail conob tuꞌ, cax max in ayapnok tꞌununok sat txꞌotxꞌ. Cacꞌal tuꞌ max yun in colchaj yul kꞌab cham tuꞌ.
Yuj tuꞌ, caxcꞌal cꞌam wal jelapnok, palta chon tzalojcꞌaltaꞌa, ta ay e yelapnok. Yetok cꞌapaxok, ok on txajlok e yuj, yet watxꞌ chi aj can watxꞌji oc e nabal.
14 abilxa wecꞌcan bay Jerusalén, cax max in toj yetok Bernabé junelxa. Max jitok Tito jetok.
A eb chi yaoc yikemal bay ley Moisés yipok cꞌul, aytek yowal cꞌul Dios yiban eb. Yujtol chi yal txꞌan Un axca tiꞌ: Catabnelayokab mactxel cꞌam chi ikencꞌal masanil tzet tzꞌibbilcan yul ley, ẍi yul txꞌan.
Caw chin oc wal il talaj nabacꞌal max in ecꞌ mulnaj e nan e xol bay tuꞌ.
Naektek, tol a jabok yich pan, pilan chi jumbi ecꞌ xol ixim harina.
Caxcꞌal chi akꞌlay circuncidar eb, palta cꞌam chi ikchaj masanil tzet chi yal ley Moisés yuj eb, palta chi yochej eb che yakꞌ circuncidar e ba, yet watxꞌ chi maynej ba eb e yin, yujtol max pol-lay oc jun yechelej tuꞌ yin e mimanil.
Yujtol asannej beybal yulyibankꞌinal tiꞌ max e beybalnej. Max e beybalnej axca yochwan nak ay yopiso yajawbi xol cakꞌekꞌ tiꞌ. Acꞌal oc jun espíritu tuꞌ chi akꞌwi cꞌulej bay eb man yikemok bay Dios tinaniꞌ.
Yuj tuꞌ, masanilcꞌal eb yajaw yayji satcan, cꞌal jantak eb chi akꞌon cuenta bay tuꞌ, yet ok yilon eb tzetbil jayji ayon yiglesia onxa tiꞌ, ok nachaj wal el yuj eb, tol xiwil ton is jelanil Dios.
Caw kꞌekkꞌinal ay is nabal eb. Cꞌam chi yakꞌ Dios jabok is kꞌinal eb tol aycꞌal yin tojbalkꞌinal, yujtol cꞌam jabok chi nachaj el yuj eb yuj is pitalil eb.
Yuj tuꞌ, chi cam jilon tzet chi el co beybalneni, manokab axcaok eb cꞌam is nabal yul sat Dios, palta ayokab co nabal.
Manak yetok junok comon anima lanan jakꞌlen owal, palta tol a yetok juntzan espíritu ay is yipalil yunen tzet man watxꞌok xol cakꞌekꞌ, a yetok eb lanan jakꞌlen owal, juntzan eb ay yopiso yin yakꞌon yajawilal, cax ayoc eb yajawilok tzet man watxꞌok bay yulyibankꞌinal tiꞌ.
yujtol wojtak, tol caxcꞌal chi wab yail tinaniꞌ, palta watxꞌ ok in elocok, yujtol lanan e txajli wuj. Watxꞌ ok in elocok yujtol ayoc Cham Yespíritu Jesucristo wetok.
Chi wochej chin chektok Timoteo tiꞌ ayex yet jayeb cꞌu, ta axca tuꞌ chi el yin cꞌul Cham Jajawil Jesús, yujtol chi wochej chi wabej tzetbil e yayji bay tuꞌ, cax chi tzaloj aj in cꞌul e yuj caytiꞌ.
Palta a eb tuꞌ, yowalil ok cꞌaycan el eb yin junelnej. Asan tzet chi yochej oc mimanil eb, asan yin tuꞌ ayoc nabal eb, axca tol is diosal eb yayji oc juntzan tuꞌ. Ay juntzan tzet chi el yunen eb, caw qꞌuixwiltak. Asan yin juntzan tuꞌ chi luesnej ba eb. Asan juntzan yet yulyibankꞌinal tiꞌ chi na eb.
Che yun axca tuꞌ, yujtol lanan e yechbanen tzet ayoc yipok e cꞌul cꞌubabil bay satcan. Atax yet max e yaben oc jun kꞌanejal yet colbanilej caw yel, atax yet tuꞌ max e chail yich e yaon oc jun tuꞌ yipok e cꞌul.
Yuj tuꞌ, axca max e yut e chaon Cham Jajawil Jesucristo, axcaokab tuꞌ che yut e beybal yul kꞌab tinaniꞌ.
Cꞌam chi jeꞌ jion ecꞌ co pak bay eb. Ta ay mac ijan chi jakꞌlej aj owal yetok, jakꞌek mimancꞌulal yin. Axca max yun yakꞌon mimancꞌulal Cham Jajawil jin, axcaokab tuꞌ chi jut jakꞌon cꞌapax mimancꞌulal.
Tiꞌ ayin wal caw Pablo in tiꞌ chin tzꞌibejtok cawil e cꞌul yetok wal in kꞌab. Naek in tek, tol preso wayji caytiꞌ. Yakꞌokabcꞌal Dios is watxꞌcꞌulal ayex bay tuꞌ.
E yujcꞌal xan caw wal watxꞌ jet, cax caw wal chon tzaloj e yuj.
Axa on mac iquis onto tiꞌ, junej ok yun jilay ajtok yetok eb, cax ok on tok xol asun yet ok co chalen co ba yetok Cham Jajawil bay nan satcan. Axa jayji ecꞌ yetok yin junelnej.
Ajun Silvano yetok Timoteo wetok ayin Pablo in tiꞌ, cax chi waontok jun carta tiꞌ ayex, ex creyente aj Tesalónica. Yet exxa co Mam Dios, yet exxa cꞌapax Cham Jajawil Jesucristo.
Chex txajli cꞌapaxok, yet watxꞌ cꞌamokab tzet chon utlay yuj eb yob is nabal, yujtol man masanilok anima chi yaoc yin cꞌul.
Caw miman watxꞌcꞌulal Cham Jajawil max txꞌox ayin. Max yakꞌ waoc in cꞌul yin, cax max yakꞌon cꞌapax in camcꞌulal, axcacꞌal chi yut yakꞌon ayon junjun on, yujtol junxanej jayji yetok Cristo Jesús.
Yowalil caw chi yaoc eb nabal yin juntzan cuybej akꞌbil ayon yuj Dios, juntzan bay chi jaoc co cꞌul. Yuj tuꞌ yowalilokab chi cha yab eb tzet chi yal yikbomal is nabal.
Palta ay eb xal camnakxa yichamil chi yakꞌ is nabal yin tzet chi yochej cꞌul. Caxcꞌal iquis eb tuꞌ yul sat anima, palta yul sat Dios camnak el eb.
Ach Timoteo, tol yet achxa Dios, ontawal juntzan tzet cꞌam watxꞌil max waltek tiꞌ. Tojolcꞌal chot a beybal. Asanokab yin Dios chaoc a cꞌul, cꞌal a nabal. Ayokab a camcꞌulal. Tecꞌbaj a ba aben yail. Yaynakil chot a ba.
Yuj tu xin, ach tol axca in cꞌajol ach, tecꞌbaj a ba yuj watxꞌcꞌulalil Dios chi yakꞌ ayon, yujtol junxanej jayji yetok Cristo Jesús.
Cꞌam jabok camcꞌulal eb, cꞌam bay ok okꞌ cꞌul eb yin junokxa mactxel. Ok wajwok kꞌanej eb. Maj jeꞌ mitxꞌon tzakay eb is mimanil. Axca wal junok no noꞌ caw ow, caytuꞌ ok yut ba eb. Ok oc eb ajcꞌulal yin masanil tzet watxꞌ.
Ilcꞌal a ba bay nak ach tiꞌ, yujtol chi yakꞌ nak ajcꞌulal yin jun abix chi jalilok.
Watxꞌ chot a beybal yin masanil yil eb. Aokab yet chach cuywaj xol eb, chach cuywaj yin masanil a cꞌul, cꞌal yin cꞌam ejmachꞌil.
Caw wal chin tzaloj oj, yujtol ay ab a camcꞌulal bay tuꞌ. Caw wal chi wiꞌ in mimancꞌulal oj caytiꞌ, yujtol ach tiꞌ wuẍtak, caw wal chakꞌ tzalojbok cꞌul eb creyente bay tuꞌ.
Chi yaoc eb is yángel yin cakꞌekꞌal. Chi ya cꞌapax oc eb yakꞌomal serbil yin xak kꞌakꞌejal, ẍi.
Ayon chon oc yuninalok Dios yetok Cristo, cambejal yayji co mimanil tiꞌ. Yuj tuꞌ xan yowalil max oc cꞌapax mimanil Jesús cambejal axca co mimanil tiꞌ, xan a yet max cam Cham, max yakꞌ lajwok jun ayoc yikbej on yakꞌon camok, a ton nak diablo.
Palta lajwinakxa mulnajil Dios yettax max lajwi watxꞌnen yulyibankꞌinal tiꞌ.
Ilab ayxa tiempoal e yaon oc yin e cꞌul. Moj wal tol cuywajwom exxa tinaniꞌ, palta acꞌalaꞌ babel cuyoj e yabnak, yowalil acꞌalaꞌ chi al-lay ayex. Manto tecꞌanok e waayi, lajan extocꞌal axca junok aqꞌuiẍ unin chito txutxwi, cꞌamto jabok tzet chi loꞌ.
A tinaniꞌ, a eb chi chaon diezmo eb jet conob, naba anima eb, cambejal yayji eb; palta chi yal txꞌan Un, tol a Melquisedec, axca tol iquisto.
Palta max yil Dios tol yob yutnak ba eb anima tuꞌ. Yuj tuꞌ xan chi yal yul txꞌan Un axca tiꞌ:
Yujtol manak yul jun templo watxꞌnebil yuj anima bay max octok Cristo, yujtol a jun tuꞌ, yenelcꞌal jun acaw templo Dios. A bay satcan, a tuꞌ max octok. A tinaniꞌ, ayicꞌ satak Dios yuj tewi juj.
Manchak co bekay co wajban co ba, axca beybal juntzan eb co xol. Yowalil chi jiptzelejek co ba. Jakꞌek jip, yujtol lanan jilon juntzan yechel chi txꞌoxon tol toxa chi jay cꞌual jayubal Cham Jajawil.
Kꞌinalok ta acꞌalaꞌ naontok eb is txꞌotxꞌal bay max ca tita, tekan max jeꞌ meltzojtok eb bay tuꞌ.
Caxcꞌal tecꞌan che yut e yajcꞌulnen e ba yetok yobtakil, palta cꞌamto chex cam yuj.
A yet chi jilen co ba yetok jetbi junjun on, ayokab yelapnok jun ilejbail tuꞌ yul co sat. Asanokab yin jetbi tuꞌ chi jaoc co nabal junjun on, yujtol a mac chi yaoc mul yul kꞌab yistzil ma yul kꞌab yichamil, ok beycꞌulnelay eb yuj Dios, cꞌal eb tol manto yetbiok ba cax chi mulji, ok beycꞌulnelay cꞌapax eb yuj Dios.
A mac chi yakꞌ cabcꞌulal, man tecꞌanok waay nabal yin tzancꞌal tzet chi yunej.
Max yalcan Dios axca tiꞌ: Manchak e yaoc e mul yul kꞌab e yetbi junjun ex. Manchak e makꞌ cam e yet animail, ẍi. A ton Dios max aloncan cabil. Yuj tu xin, caxcꞌal tol cꞌam chon mulji, palta tatol chi jakꞌ cam junok jet animail, chi yal elapnok xin, tol mayal co ten tzet chi yal jun ley tuꞌ.
Tatol caytuꞌ che yut e ba, manak bay Dios chi tit jun e jelanilal tu xin, titol yet sat txꞌotxꞌ tiꞌ, yet eb comon anima. A jun e jelanilal tuꞌ, yet nak diablo chi yal tuꞌ.
Ex wuẍtak, ex wanab, a eb max alon el kꞌanej Dios yet payxa, max techaj wal yuj eb yiklen oc yatakilal, cax max yakꞌon eb mimancꞌulal. Yuj tu xin, techajokab e yuj axca eb tuꞌ.
A yet manto yesnej aj Dios yulyibankꞌinal tiꞌ, nabilxa yuj tol caytuꞌ ok yun yelol yiban Cristo. Palta ato yet juntzan lajub tiempoal tiꞌ max alaytek, yet chi txecloj el bay yulyibankꞌinal tiꞌ yuj co watxꞌilok.
Kꞌinalok yuj junok tzet yob max el juneni cax chon makꞌlay tinaniꞌ, ¿xin ta yujcꞌal ok jakꞌ techaj jun yailal tuꞌ xan watxꞌ on? Palta kꞌinalok ta comoncꞌal chi alay oc yailal jiban yuj junok tzet watxꞌ chi el junen tinaniꞌ, ta chi jakꞌ techaj jun yailal tuꞌ, a ton jun tuꞌ watxꞌ yul sat Dios.
Yuj tu xin, axcaokab tuꞌ chi jut co ba, yet watxꞌ aokab tzet chi chaꞌ cꞌul Dios chi junej, yakꞌban tol ayon ecꞌ bay yulyibankꞌinal tiꞌ. Manchakxa junej axca chi yochej oc co mimanil tiꞌ.
A juẍtak Silvano tiꞌ, wojtakxa is nabal, caw wal puch yikem. Aꞌ ok iontok jun in carta tiꞌ ayex. A jay belan kꞌanej max waltok tiꞌ, a ok iptzen e nabal. A caw wal is watxꞌcꞌulalil Dios jun chi wal yabixal tiꞌ. Tecꞌancꞌal che yut e ba yin is watxꞌcꞌulalil tiꞌ.
Yetok cꞌapaxok, yanaktek Dios is cꞌaybanilal el eb aj Sodoma yetok eb aj Gomorra. Pilan lajwinak el cab conob tuꞌ, max tzꞌatok yuj kꞌakꞌej. Tanxacꞌal max yuncantok masanil. A eb lajwinak el tuꞌ, is txꞌoxbanilok eb cꞌam Dios yul sat.
Ex in camcꞌulnebil, lanan jechbanen jay juntzan mayal waltek tiꞌ. Yuj tuꞌ xan jakꞌek jip, yet watxꞌ cꞌamokab jabok co yobtakil cꞌal jabok co paltail yul sat Cham yet jun cꞌual tuꞌ. Tatol axca tuꞌ, juncꞌulalxacꞌal ay on yetok Cham.
Cꞌamokab co camcꞌulnejek co ba yetok yulyibankꞌinal tiꞌ, tamwal yetok juntzan tzetak yetal ay bay yulyibankꞌinal tiꞌ. Ta chi co camcꞌulnelej co ba yetok, cꞌamxa co camcꞌulal yin co Mam Dios chi yal tuꞌ.
Jojtak tzetbil yayji oc is camcꞌulal Dios jin, tol max yakꞌ ba Jesucristo cam juj. Yuj tuꞌ, yowalil cayokab tuꞌ chi jut co camcꞌulnen eb juẍtak, eb janab, jakꞌokab co ba cam qꞌuexelok eb.
Aꞌ ayon chi jaoc yin co cꞌul tol a Jesús, a ton Cristo, ayon ton yuninal onxa Dios. Kꞌinalok tinaniꞌ, ta chi co camcꞌulnej junok mamej, chi co camcꞌulnej cꞌapax eb is yuninal.
Ta che kꞌan is watxꞌcꞌulal Dios yiban, axca wal tol che yaltok e yet yin is cuybej man watxꞌok tuꞌ yetok.
Axca wal yipal yaj pomnaj sat aꞌ mar, cay wal tuꞌ eb, yujtol cꞌamxa chi tenchanej ba eb yin yobtakil. Axca wal sukuwal aꞌ chi elcan tilak aꞌ, inej oc kꞌalem, cay wal tuꞌ eb, yuj juntzan tzet qꞌuixwiltak chi yun tuꞌ. Kꞌinalok ay junok waycan chi cꞌaytok yin is be, caytuꞌ eb. Yowalil ok apnok eb xol kꞌekkꞌinal yin junelnej, cax ok ayjok ecꞌ eb bay tuꞌ yin tojbalkꞌinal.
Tzꞌibejcan juntzan tzet mayal el tiꞌ, juntzan ayicꞌ yet jun tiempoal tiꞌ, cꞌal juntzan tolto ok ujok.
¡Masanilcꞌal mac chi aben juntzan tiꞌ, yacbajokab eb txiquin bay tzet chi yal Cham Espíritu bay junjun iglesia! cha tzꞌibejtok, ẍi Jesús.
A jun babel, lajan yili axca yili junok no coj. A jun yet is cab, lajan yili axca junok achꞌej wacax. A jun yet is yox, lajan yili sat axca yili sat anima. Axa jun yet is can xin, lajan yili axca junok no águila chi ecꞌ jenenok.
Ay junxa chej, cakyin yili max wilaꞌ. A jun mac ayaj yiban jun chej tuꞌ, max chaꞌ is yikbej yin yion el juncꞌulal bay masanil yulyibankꞌinal, cax chi yakꞌlen cam ba anima. Ay jun miman espada max akꞌlay bay.
Yuj tuꞌ, ayicꞌ eb satak is trono Dios bay is templo. Cacꞌal tiꞌ yakꞌwi serbil eb bay tuꞌ yet cꞌualil cꞌal yet akꞌbalil. Axa Cham chotan ay yul is trono tuꞌ chi taynen eb, yujtol aycꞌal ecꞌ yetok eb.
Axa toj xuyon el eb canwan ángel tuꞌ, yet chi toj eb makꞌoj cam anima. Txenxa maj nanjok cam anima yuj eb bay sat txꞌotxꞌ. Txequelxa is yorail, is cꞌual, is xajawil cꞌal is yabilal yet chi oc eb yin makꞌoj cam anima.
Yuj tuꞌ xan ok tok eb xol jun asun bay satcan tuꞌ. Toxacꞌal tꞌanan ajtok eb ajcꞌul tuꞌ yin eb.
A jun chi yik Noꞌ max wil tuꞌ, lajan yili axca junok no mimek tzꞌib coj. Lajan yakan axca yakan no oso. Lajan tiꞌ axca tiꞌ no coj. Max yakꞌ no dragón is yikbej bay, cax max yaon oc Noꞌ yin yajawilal is qꞌuexelok. Miman yikbej Noꞌ max yakꞌ bay.
Max lajwi tuꞌ, max waben yoc jun aw bay satcan. Max yalon ayin axca tiꞌ: Tzꞌibej junxa tzet ok wal ayach tiꞌ: A tinaniꞌ, caw watxꞌ yet eb aycꞌal oc yul kꞌab Cham Yajaw, cax chi cami, cha tzꞌibej, ẍi jun aw tuꞌ.
Lajwi tuꞌ, cax max secon ay jun yet is wak ángel tzet ayay yul is secꞌ yiban aꞌ miman aej chi yik Éufrates. Max tanaj aꞌ Éufrates tuꞌ, yuj yoc is be aꞌ tuꞌ beok eb yajaw ok tit bay chi ajol cꞌu.
¡Mayal wal aycꞌay conob Babilonia, cꞌam junok axca, palta mayal aycꞌayi! Mayal oc cajlubok eb espíritu yob. Mayal occan bay chi wajbaj ba junjun makan eb espíritu yob. Mayal occan wayubok no tzꞌiquin caw yajbejtak, tol man watxꞌok.
¡Aleluya! A co Diosal max akꞌon co colbanil. Caw miman yelapnok Cham, miman cꞌapax yipalil Cham.
A eb yet-xa Cristo, a eb tuꞌ babel ictzonebil ajok. (Axa juntzanxa eb camnak xin, majto ictzonelay aj eb, masantacꞌal yet max lajwi mil abil tuꞌ.)
A chꞌen mimek chꞌen aycan aytok yichok tuꞌ, xiwil chꞌen chꞌen can is tojol ayoc yelbubok. A chꞌen babel, jaspecꞌal el ayoc yelbubok. Chꞌen yet is cab, safiro. Chꞌen yet is yox, ágata. Chꞌen yet is can, esmeralda.
Yakꞌokab Cham Jajawil Jesús is watxꞌcꞌulal ayon co masanil.
